            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>Author: Yi Tarng Wu</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: April 27, 2008 [EBook #25195]</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK FENG YUEH JIANN ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Hui-Ting Chuang</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\"> 校點說明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    《風月鑒》一書，系清代吳貽棠所作。吳貽棠，字蔭南，號愛存</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，河南戈陽（今河南光山縣）人。該書刻本稱其為吳貽先。我們根據</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>書前作者自序及書后其寄男方鈺的跋文，可以約略的知道他的經歷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>其生活于乾嘉年間，“為人好脫略，性豪邁”，曾“仕長蘆”。回鄉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>后得痿疾，行動不便，于岑寂中作《可是夢》、《風月鑒》二書，以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>寄無聊之慨。《可是夢》今已不傳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    該書有刻本和抄本兩種。嘉慶刻本，今北京圖書館和天津圖書館</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>均有收藏，半頁六行，每行十六字，第十三回有半頁殘缺。抄本第十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>三、十四回均殘，版式與刻本相同，今藏于浙江圖書館。上海古籍出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>版社曾以殘抄本為底本，用刻本第十三、十四回加以補配，作為《古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>本小說集成》的一種影印出版。本次點校，即以影印本為依據。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">敘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    余于戊寅冬得痿疾，閱三載而未就痊，起坐雖可，維不倩人，而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>步履維艱矣。鎮日獨坐甚覺岑寂。時文侄可村、甥居亭皆課于余家，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>每為小談。余告之曰：“如余，將何以自處也？”可村曰：“先生胡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不評論蒼鳥以自娛兮？”居亭亦曰：“甚善。”余則自思：左手憊矣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，右手雖尚可磨墨拈筆，然意亂心煩，何能修事筆硯乎？自念蒼鳥文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>章，自古累累繁帙，后之所作者，即珍句奇字，亦不過拾古人牙慧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>且余之才，夫何敢與騷人文士馳騁而較邪？若風月佳話，余則有聞之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>古人者，有見之今人者。余固非鐘于情者，竊欲以深情者、過情者、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>纏綿于情不可解者，又有用情而迷于情、傷于情者，余置之以供余之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>閑情。或曰余不知情者，余不問也。余之是編，有謂為言之有自者，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>非也；有謂為言之無自者，亦非也；有謂為在有自無自之間者，更非</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也。余不過一時信筆略去耳，又何自之足言也！此編成，余招可村、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>居亭觀之。可村曰：“時值炎夏矣，可為消暑之一策。”居亭曰：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>悶坐無聊矣，可為清遣之一方。”余即志之。自為序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>                   嘉慶庚辰夏仲，愛牖民言略于茹芝小堂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第一回  投胎  解笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    古來聖賢學問生而知之者，固不待言；其次亦莫非由閱歷而成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>然古來聖賢之閱歷，無非多嘗艱苦、履霜堅冰，而后始成。一代偉人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，未聞有從溫柔鄉里、歡樂場練出一番胸襟來的。豈知不然。我閑同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>友人談論，得聞一件奇事。今于茶前酒后，磨墨拈筆記出來，以為閑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>談。至于其事能傳不能傳，我亦不問了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    昔南京雨花台西，有一家姓常名興，其妻鄭氏。這家本是歷代簪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>纓相傳，是明季常遇春之后。現在家中良田萬頃，還有幾處當典。這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>常興之父是山東道台，常興卻是守祖上余業，也無心仕路，日日在家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>好善，凡鄉中貧苦，無不周濟。只是上天不佑，善人至六旬無子。一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日，至一友家，聞說杭州天竺寺菩薩極靈。常興就動了念頭，想去求</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子。就擇了日子、雇了船，上杭州去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了杭州，尋了店住下，候到朔日，備了香紙，往天竺去燒香。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>由城至寺有三十里遠，一路香客絡絡不斷。常興到了寺，將香紙燒了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，恭恭敬敬拜了幾拜，起來瞻仰菩薩，才知這菩薩是沉香雕成的。又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>往別處看玩景致，忽聽一眾人說：“那里一個和尚真真奇怪，如何要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>死，還說要等施主？”常興聽了，也同著眾人去看。見那和尚瞑目而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>坐，卻也奇怪，至常興到了，他睜眼一看，說：“來得好，我去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”就死了。常興看著可憐，就拿幾兩銀子替他買木頭殯葬了。從寺回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來，到店又住了一日，才回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了家，鄭氏接著。敘了一會燒香的話，又說起和尚的事。鄭氏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>合掌念道：“阿彌陀佛！此事做的好。”鄭氏原是常興續娶的，才四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>十多歲，所以過了半月，似乎有胎。常興知道，甚是喜歡，日日叫他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>休養，莫要沖動胎氣，又吩咐丫頭們不許有事大驚小怪的驚動了奶奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。不覺到了十個月，一日，鄭氏腹內覺疼。常興叫家人去請了穩婆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>守到半夜，生下來了。常興一聽小孩子哭，就問是男是女，丫頭說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“恭喜大爺，是個哥兒。”常興歡喜非常。到了三朝，請了前前后后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>許多的客是不必說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    只是這孩子卻奇的很，自生下來哭了一陣之后，不時的就笑。常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>興說：“這是何故？”因他大總無子，以先生了兩個都亡了，這個又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是求來的，真真就象掌上珍珠一般。不把他當個男呂子，把他當個女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>孩，又因他肯笑，就起個名字叫嫣娘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    這嫣娘生來淘氣，自小便不喜歡老媽子抱他。若是年幼的抱他，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他有說有笑；老媽子抱他，他雖是肯笑，一見老媽子就是哭。到四五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歲，便不必說了，見了女人年紀大的就象仇人似的；見了小女孩子同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他頑他就歡歡喜喜，他吃的不吃，給那女孩子吃，頑的不頑，給那女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>孩子頑。常興也就隨著兒子，給他買了兩個丫頭。一個與他同歲，起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>名叫嫿姐，長的長長的臉，一道細細的眉，一個小嘴就像點了胭脂一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>般，瘦瘦的身子，扎著兩個丫角。露著青青的頭皮。一個大他一歲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起名叫娟姐，長的圓圓的臉，也是細細的眉，兩個眼秋波兒似的，也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>扎著丫角，身子也是瘦瘦的。常興買來，又給他換了一身綢緞衣服，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫他天天去伴著嫣娘。哪知嫣娘一見面就親熱的了不得。就是旁人惹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>惱了他，他兩個一去說，就笑起來了。鄭氏想著，只這兩個丫頭伴著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，他太寂寞些，又買兩個小的。俱小嫣娘幾歲，一個叫關關，一個叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窈窈，俱是如畫的小美女。嫣娘見了，是不必說的更是親熱的了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了八歲，嫣娘越大越淘氣。常興就請位先生，叫他上學。日日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還是他四個陪著他去讀書。他卻又奇怪，凡書一目了然；只是他四個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>好，一個不在跟前，他就連扁擔長的“一”字也不識，常興只得依從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，叫他四個陪著，一連讀了三年。到了十一歲上，他就說：“不讀罷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>！我都會了。”常興說：“你豈可閑著？”嫣娘說：“俺家現有一處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大花園，我就在那里自己讀書，豈不大妙！”未知常興允不允。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">第二回  幻夢  刁宴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘要到園里讀書，常興就叫人去收拾了。擇了日子，叫嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘搬進花園。又想著園子大了，他們小孩子住著害怕，就叫些女家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>靠近住著，又叫了幾個二十多歲的丫頭去作伴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘日日在園內一處一處的游玩，連書篇兒也不摸，一日頑乏了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，睡了午覺，就作了一夢。夢見到一仙山，其中樓閣玲瓏，如珠玉修</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>成的一般。信步走去，忽見一門，就大著膽走進去，見是三間花閣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>垂著湘妃竹的帘子。猛聽得一陣笑聲，如鶯聲嬌囀，不覺腳跟下走了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>三魂七魄，站在那里就呆了。忽有一個人從背后輕輕拍他一下，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“看什么！好大膽！”嫣娘聽了這一句話就像小鶯兒叫了一聲，想道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“就在屋里，如何又到這里來了？”連忙轉過身來，作了一揖，才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>抬頭去看。那人帶嗔呼道：“低下頭去。”嫣娘就不敢仰視，只順著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>眼看見﹝那人﹞穿著銀杏衫子，罩著墨色撒花背心，穿著百摺百蝶裙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子，一對蓮鉤只露出一個尖兒。嫣娘也不敢出聲，只彎著腰站著。站</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了一時，那人說：“還不快去！”嫣娘慢慢出了門，才敢回頭來看，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卻不見那人了，只聽帘內說：“好好談談。”嫣娘也不敢再聽，又往</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>前走，又見一帶花障。他從垂花門進去，見一美人在廊下，背著臉向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>內坐著，在那里讀詩，其聲微微莫辦。他就偷偷的到背后，一看卻不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是讀詩，是在那里拈著筆寫甚么。嫣娘順著他寫的看去，是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    天上人間，可憐誰是前緣，誰是無緣？到頭來，那是一般參了個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>無要緊的禪，才笑人枉然。作一對鴛鴦睡，誰知我，也是空纏綿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘看畢，不覺一聲嘆道：“可憐可憐！斯言誠不謬也。”那人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>回頭一看，嫣娘才自想道：“不好，我如何竟走近他身子跟前了？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>只得連忙作揖。那人卻不怪他，只說：“你去罷，此地非久停之所。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘又作了一個揖，就出來了。走著又回頭偷偷一看，見那花容月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>貌，世間罕有，又不敢長看，只得一直出去。卻一路走一路想，不覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>防著，就一頭碰在一個粉牆上，撞在地下坐著，只聽后邊有一兩個人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嗤嗤的笑。嫣娘起來，那一兩個美人也走到跟前了。嫣娘就拱手而立</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，說：“得罪，得罪，有勞尊笑！”那美人說：“這個人必是呆子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>自己頭不疼，還給我們周旋。”又一個美人說：“莫是個瘋子，我們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>走罷！”嫣娘也不敢出聲，只是呆呆望著那﹝兩﹞人說說笑笑去了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>才想起來：“是他們罵我！”只得又走。忽見又一大門，他又進去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>順著腳走到一處小花園，看著兩個美人在那里打秋千。嫣娘就走到那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>玲瓏石旁站著，說：“小心些，掉下來就了不得了！”那打秋千的只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>顧忽上忽下，卻不看見旁邊站著有人，聽他說話才看見，說：“你是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何人？怎么來到這里？”嫣娘說：“我是嫣娘。”那人笑了一笑，說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我又知道你是個甚么嫣娘？但是你是個男人，如何叫女人名字？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘方欲回話，那秋千架上的人也下來了，說：“姐姐，莫跟他說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。這必是個小賊子，將他鎖起來！”嫣娘說：“好，好，就是這樣玩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>法。”那一個說：“這是個傻子，趕出去就是了！”嫣娘只當與他說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頑話，還是笑。那人說：“你再不出去，就打了！”嫣娘只得笑著出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了。不妨地下青苔甚滑，一下跌倒。猛然驚醒，卻是一夢。他卻不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>把這當個夢，一心要去訪這些美人。他又不敢直向常興說，日日在園</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>中納悶。雖有他四個陪著，總不能解他的悶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，他四個商議說：“嫣娘天天似乎心里有事，俺們今日大家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>備個菜，請他吃酒。等他醉后，問問他。”他四個商議定了，第二日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就向嫣娘說：“俺四個有個薄酌，請大爺吃一杯，不知可賞小的們的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>臉？”嫣娘說：“你們成天家想著法鬧，又請甚么客？又是甚么小的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大的的？我是個豬八戒淨壇使者，豈有不好吃的！好菜好酒，快些拿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來，等我狼餐虎咽。”關關說：“只怕不是狼虎，是個小雛燕子！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫿姐說：“也不是個雛燕，是個小學生、假姑娘！”娟姐說：“我前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日跟奶奶往王表爺家聽戲，唱的是《請宴》，只怕大相公就是那請宴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上的秀才們，‘聞道請，似得了將軍令，宛是五臟神，願隨鞭鐙。’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”。窈窈說：“大相公明日去中個學，就是秀才了。”嫣娘說：“真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>真你們是些女孩子，不知外面的事。如何進學說是中學，若中舉、中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>進士，豈不也要說進舉進進士嗎？”大家說著笑起來，把窈窈倒羞的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>滿臉通紅。嫣娘看著甚不過意，就照自己嘴上打了一巴掌，說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>可混說了？”嫿姐說：“我說個情，饒他這一次，下次重重的打罷！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“不是嫿姐說情，真個不饒！”關關就上去替嫣娘揉揉嘴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，說：“你看，都打紅了。”娟姐說：“莫鬧了，擺桌子罷。”說著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>將桌子擺開，上面設了一張大椅。嫣娘說：“怎么只用一張？”嫿姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我們這奴才，如何敢坐？”嫣娘陡然變了色，說：“我幾時有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這些混帳的意思，如何說小的、又說奴才？豈不是折罪我嗎？我一定</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>少活十年。”嫿姐說：“莫急。這是我們的話，與你不相干。你要氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我，給你賠個禮！”說著就拜了一拜。嫣娘笑著說：“不敢，不敢！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我受你一拜，更要少活二十年！”關關說：“你看，媽媽們送菜來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。坐下罷！等我去接進來。若是等他們送上來，你又嫌俺臟了。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“豈無個陪客，豈無個主人？依我說，我就領擾；不依我說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我就要辭謝了！”他四個說：“依了就是。”嫣娘說：“我今日是你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們請的客，就大膽僭了。陪我的次坐是娟姐，三坐是嫿姐，主坐就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關關、窈窈姐。這是序齒，最公道的。”他四個都無的說，就依次坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>下了。關關說：“我來回上菜。”窈窈說：“我來把盞。”大家坐著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說了一會，飲了一會。嫿姐想醉嫣娘，叫他好說實話，就使個眼色給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窈窈。窈窈說：“我小些，我要敬一杯！”拿了一個瑪瑙六方杯子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>滿斟了一杯，送到嫣娘面前。嫣娘說：“多謝！這是必領的。”就三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>口兩口吃完了，說：“小弟不敢有慢尊命，飲畢了。”關關說：“再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小些就是我了，我也奉敬一杯，不知尊意如何？”嫣娘笑著說：“願</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>領，願領。”關關就拿了一個翡翠圓杯，滿斟了送上去，嫣娘也三口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩口吃完了，說：“覆命，吃完了。”娟姐、嫿姐也想敬他，又怕太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>吃醉了。嫿姐說：“我是五歲來你家的，”又指著娟姐說：“他是六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歲來的，”又指著關關、窈窈說：“他兩個也是五、六歲上來的，來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>到都跟你在一塊。我們今日飲酒，各人有各人的心思，都說說。就先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>從相公說起。”嫣娘總不出聲，嫿姐們總是要他說。不知說了未說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第三回  戲墨  誤宴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘只是不說，窈窈就想個法兒哄他，向嫣娘說：“前日你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>睡著了，好說夢話，我都聽著了，甚么這一個那一個的？”嫣娘只當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是真的，就站起來說：“你還說他怎么，真叫人到如今放不下！”娟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐說：“這我們不知道。你何不說出來，我們大家替你想想，還是怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么好！”嫣娘想了一想，又笑了一笑，說：“我向你們說罷！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    正在要說，一個丫頭進來說：“奶奶來了！”嫣娘連忙出來接著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。鄭氏進來，說：“嫣娘，你天天可有念念書？”嫣娘聽了，不敢說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>沒有，只是笑。嫿姐代答說：“白日相公一天總寫一千字，燈下書也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>念四五本。”關關說：“俺四個都是陪著相公天天到三更才睡。”鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏說：“像這樣才好。你父說不久要叫你去過府考，明日先去府里候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，”又向娟姐說：“你大些，好好把相公的衣服被褥收拾收拾，明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日好去，”又向嫿姐、關關、窈窈說：“你們也幫著。”此四個一齊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>答應著：“是！”鄭氏說：“我去了，你們收拾罷！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘又送到院里才回來。嫣娘說：“你們怎么不替我快快收拾，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還站著？”娟姐說：“方才你的話不未說完。”嫣娘說：“這時候我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也顧不得說了，等考完了來家再說罷。”又叫娟、嫿二人去收拾行李</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又叫關關拿書本，又叫窈窈磨墨。關關、窈窈忙著去拿書的拿書，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>磨墨的磨墨。關關把古文四書五經、時文律賦律詩搬了一堆，堆在嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘面前。嫣娘看了一看，也未打開，笑了一笑說：“這從哪里念的起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？不念罷！”窈窈又把墨也磨了一硯池，嫣娘走過去，看著他磨墨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窈窈只顧磨，未見嫣娘走來。嫣娘就伸手把墨抹了一指頭，抹了窈窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一臉。窈窈把墨放下，叫著說：“你這個相公！罷了，罷了。我替你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>磨墨，你不酬我的勞，還抹我一臉墨！”嫣娘笑的氣喘不過來，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“你這個人不識好，你們天天擦些甚么石灰，抹的像死人一樣。我替</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你想個新樣的妝扮，還不好看些嗎？”窈窈瞅著嫣娘，說：“好看好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>看，多謝多謝！”嫣娘說：“把硯瓦也收起來罷。”窈窈說：“不是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要寫字嗎？”嫣娘說：“離考的日子還早，忙些什么！”窈窈說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這不瞎忙了半天嗎？”說著就將墨放下不磨了。嫣娘又叫關關：“把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>書也收起來罷。”關關說：“不念了嗎？”嫣娘說：“念完了。”關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關說：“你連他的面也不曾見，就說念完了，我看你明日進場，將什</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么字寫在卷子上？”嫣娘聽著他說，看看指頭上的墨還未抹完，就趁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關關不防，又抹了他一臉，說：“我且把你這頭一篇批點批點。”關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關又是氣，又是笑，說：“明日你進場做不上來，學院打你一百戒尺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，也罷了！”正在鬧著，娟、嫿兩個從里間屋出來，看著一個一個的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>滿臉黑墨，笑的彎了腰，說：“今日唱《李逵打店》，怎么又有兩個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>李逵？”他兩個正在笑，嫣娘又偷偷的去把墨抹了兩手，走到娟姐背</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>后向臉上一抹，笑著說：“也叫你唱個胡敬德！”娟姐才要回頭，嫿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐站在娟姐跟前，看著大笑，不妨娟姐向旁一轉，一下歪在嫿姐身上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，都倒在地下。嫣娘笑著說：“好，好，我也替你畫畫眉。”說著把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫿姐眼上著手指頭畫了兩個圈，說：“這是個奇妝。人家的眉毛是長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的，你這是團的！”他兩個起來就要膈肢他，嫣娘一溜煙跑了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    他四個叫了丫頭們端了水來，洗了臉。洗完了，你給我看，我給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你看，看墨可有了。關關說：“我們真是糊涂，何不把大鏡子拿出來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，大家照照就是了！”正要去拿鏡子，嫣娘走進來，站在當中，作了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一個揖，說：“有罪，有罪！唐突西子，該領巴掌八個！”娟姐說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“我們一個人打一巴掌罷！”嫣娘說：“不好。若是只打一巴掌，諸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>位的那只手豈不又怪我偏心嗎？”嫿姐說：“好好坐著罷，養養神，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>明日好上府。”嫣娘說：“正為明日遠別，今日不可不細細談談。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關關說：“老天，老天，怎么了？這離府里好有二千步，就說遠別，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>后來你做了官，要是四川、廣西，還說個甚么別呢？這個‘遠’字，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我要是個試官，就打一百個杠子！”嫣娘就向關關作個揖，說：“門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>生領教。”嫿姐說：“莫鬧了，屋里黑了還未點燈，叫他們點燈罷！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”遂叫了丫環來把里間屋里的燈點上，又把外間燈點上。嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這黑魆魆的，像地牢一樣。”娟姐說：“快點蠟來！”嫣娘笑了一笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我明日就到府里去了，你們今日午上請我，我就還席。這個帖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是‘即夕恭候台光’。”嫿姐說：“老實些罷，又還什么席呢？”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘不肯，就叫丫頭們把正中挂的四個玻璃燈點上，又叫丫頭們去預備</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>二十六個小果碟子，十六個小吃碟子，外只要四個大碗就夠了。正在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>忙著擺桌子椅子，一個丫頭進來說：“爺請相公到上房去說話。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“真真天不隨今願了！”就沒精打的跟著來的丫頭去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了上房，常興叫嫣娘坐下，說：“俺這里離貢院雖不甚遠，然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>臨場總覺忙亂。我叫人向秦淮后街賃了一個寓處，我明日同你去。也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不知你這幾年可有個學問沒有？今年人頑了一大年，在園里，不知可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有念一句書，寫一個字沒有？”嫣娘也不敢出聲，鄭氏說：“我聽他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們說，他倒天天念天天寫，不知真假。”常興說：“只怕都是打伙的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>淘氣，他們替他裝臉，哄你天天念書寫字罷！”鄭氏說：“這明日去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>考，就知道他念不念、寫不寫了。”嫣娘心里記挂著回園請客，又不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>敢就走，聽了鄭氏的話，趁勢說：“我回園念書去罷。”常興說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這時候用功也遲了。我買的好鱖魚，叫他們已經蒸了，就在這里吃飯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>罷。”嫣娘不敢說回去，只得答應著。常興又向他說了一回場里的規</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>矩，又叫他明日進場不用忙著出來，“好好做文章，這府考完了就院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>考了，我回你也不回來，就在寓處住著。”說了一會，到三更天，丫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭才回說：“魚了，”常興說：“拿酒來。”丫頭們擺了桌椅，送上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>魚來并別的幾樣菜。常興同鄭氏坐了，叫嫣娘也坐下。吃了一會，嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘哪有心吃，說：“我今早念了一篇生文章，未背過來，我回去再念</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>念。”常興說：“不念罷，明日再念。”一時飯吃畢了，又敘了一會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>話。到交四更，鄭氏說：“天不早了，去睡罷。”嫣娘聽說，就忙忙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的回園來了。不知請客沒請。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第四回  辭艷  尋芳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘到了園里，進了屋，見外間的挂燈俱未點，問說：“怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么挂燈不點？”又問：“菜備齊沒有？”娟姐說：“天已四更多了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我們都要睡了。相公的盛饌我們心領罷。”嫣娘說：“如何使得？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫿姐、關關、窈窈俱說：“夜深了，要睡了。”嫣娘不肯，娟、嫿兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個將嫣娘推著往里間去，說：“睡罷！誰再混鬧，罰他跪一夜。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘沒法，只得進了里間。娟姐、嫿姐將門閂上，關關說：“還有窈姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>沒進來，且相公也未喝茶，我出去將茶壺拿進來。”剛要出來，窈窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了。關關說：“來的好，你就隨手將茶壺帶來。”窈窈將茶壺拿進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來，關關才閂上了門。大家都睡了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二日，一早嫣娘還在睡著，關關、窈窈也在睡著，娟、嫿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個在床上才披衣坐起，就聽有丫頭來說：“還沒起來嗎？爺叫你們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>收拾行李。”娟姐連忙穿好了衣服，開了門。嫿姐也穿了衣服，下了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>床，叫醒了關關、窈窈。嫣娘也醒了，看看他們說：“天還未明，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們都起來做甚么？”娟姐說：“太陽三竿了，爺著人來叫你哩！”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘聽說，連忙起來。娟姐就叫丫頭們舀了洗臉水。嫣娘洗了臉，就跟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著來的丫頭到上房去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    見了常興、鄭氏，說了一會話，又吃了點心，嫣娘想著：“我這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就去了，還未去辭謝他四個，”又不敢直說，心里想了一個法，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“我的書與筆硯還未收好，他們也未必知道，還得我自己去看看。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>常興說：“你會看看收好，吃了飯就走了。”嫣娘答應著，出來三步</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩步，連忙跑到園里，一進門就高聲說道：“我回來了，我可也回來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娟、嫿、關、窈接著，說：“怎么又來了？我們才想一時去送你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”嫣娘聽了，一只手拉著娟姐，一只手拉著嫿姐，就大哭起來。娟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、嫿替他拭眼淚，關關勸說：“這何必這個樣？”嫣娘聽了這一句話</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，大總的慟起來，過了一時，才說：“我去也罷。我想你們，我心里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也罷了。你們想我，費了你們的心，我實在過不去。”說著又哭。娟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、嫿同關關只是勸，也不覺淌起眼淚來，勸了一會才住下。又聽著里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>間屋有個人也在那里嗚嗚的哭，娟姐說：“這是誰個？”關關說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必是窈窈，我看著他方才紅著眼圈兒跑進屋里去了。”嫣娘連忙也進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>屋里來，向窈窈說：“莫哭罷！”一句未說完，又哭起來了。娟姐同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關關又才勸住，又勸住了窈窈，大家無言對坐。坐了一時，還是娟姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大些，想著這不是個常法，就向嫣娘說：“我想著這時候上頭的飯也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>好了，相公上去罷。”嫣娘又拉拉娟姐的手，又扯扯嫿姐的手，又看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著關關、窈窈，想說笑，嗓子卻硬了，只落﹝得﹞點點頭，恰好丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來請他，就慢慢地去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    見了常興，常興說：“你哭甚么？”嫣娘說：“沒有哭，是方才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>迷了眼揉出淚來的。”常興也不再問，﹝一﹞時同他吃了飯，叫家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>押著十幾付挑子先去了。隨后常興同嫣娘坐轎去了。娟、嫿、關、窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來送自不必說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了寓處，常興叫家人安放好了行李，又叫家人替相公擺上書桌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又叫家人打聽幾時考期。家人去了一時，回來說：“考期是第四日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”常興說：“你們去替相公備場務、買卷子，早早的辦齊。”家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>答應著去了。日日常興叫嫣娘讀書寫字是不必說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了場期，常興送他進了場。到放頭場，他就出來了。常興問說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“文章可好？”嫣娘說：“取是必取的。”又過了一日，放了榜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>常興叫家人去看，一時回來說：“取了第五。”又復試了幾場，俱在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>十名之內；放了正案，又是第五。常興一面著人去家里送信，一面叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人送嫣娘進衙門謁見老公祖。嫣娘回來，常興就叫他在寓處看書，候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著院試。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，常興有一親戚家請他吃午飯，常興去了。嫣娘寫了一會字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，想到：“前面是秦淮河，我何不去看看？”就不給家人知道，偷偷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的去了。走到秦淮河沿，一眼望去，兩岸俱是硃紅小欄杆圍著，欄內</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>或是月窗，或是六角小門，俱挂著湘妃竹的帘子。河里的小船亦不一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>樣，或是小字欄杆，或是十三女兒欄杆，又挂著各色玻璃燈毬。嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>想著：“我何不叫只小船，上去坐著逛逛。”正好來了一只小船，嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘叫﹝到﹞了近沿，上了船，一路逛去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    秦淮河里的船，原沒有男人撐船的，這只船也是兩個二十內外的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>美人撐著。嫣娘上了船，船上的美人問道：“往哪里去？”嫣娘說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“隨你撐，逛完才回來。”這兩個美人開了船，一路慢慢的撐去。嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘在船中左一看，右一看，真是“在山陰道上，目不及賞，應接不暇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也。”分不出來哪一處第一，只眼里看的俱是如花如玉，耳朵里聽的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>俱是玉笛珍琴。不知不覺，船到了夫子廟。這兩岸的街道都﹝看﹞完</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，又回來慢慢的撐著。嫣娘看著左邊一個大大的月窗，題著“天然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”二字。嫣娘叫靠著這邊住了船，又聽著“丁東，丁東”的響。嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>原會彈琴，隨站在船頭聽去，彈的是《虞美人》，又聽他的宮弦忽然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聲高，又聽著宮忽轉商，悠悠揚揚，真是如泣如訴。嫣娘不覺也掉下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>幾點眼淚，又怕撐船的看著，連忙拭去，心里想道：“這個人到是鐘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>于情者，不可不見見。”又想：“這隔著如此高，怎么上去？”就問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了船家，撐船的說：“相公要是上去，就叫人放梯子下來。”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“就煩你叫一聲。”撐船的叫應了上頭放了梯子下來。撐船的說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“相公上去可以就從前門去了。前門就是秦淮后街。”嫣娘說：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還未帶銀子來給你船錢，我送你個東西罷。”說著，將手上玉鐲去下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，賞了撐船的，就上梯子去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    上來就是月窗跟前，隔著帘子一望，望著那里邊一個人還在彈琴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，映著帘子，真像煙籠芍藥一般。這里放梯子的人將梯子收上去，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要進去，向那人說好出來迎接。嫣娘拱拱手，就站在窗外，聽他一曲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>彈完了。那人也看著窗外有人，就出來迎進去。嫣娘進去一看，那個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>美人尚在綠鬢初女，不覺大驚，想道：“如此妙點，如此妙技，可敬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>可敬，可羨可羨！我在他旁邊站一時，也不枉虛生一世。”嫣娘看著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、想著，就來﹝到﹞了﹝那美人身邊﹞，那美人說：“相公請坐！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說：“這般仙府，豈可容我濁物站在這里，還恐有玷清秀，如何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>敢坐？”美人說：“相公真是君子也，毋乃木謙乎！”就讓著坐下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘問說：“請問妙字？”美人答說：“不敢，賤名宜人。”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“妙哉，妙哉！真無不宜也。還請問妙齡？”美人答說：“十二。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘大驚，說：“奇哉，奇哉！與我同庚矣。”又說：“請問此處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>即是宜卿一人乎？”宜人說：“妾乃吾母之少女也，不曾學倚門賣笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，此為吾之側室，不意相公簫史下顧，妾非美玉，何敢勞尊？”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“宜卿所言，吾此時，一些魂魄俱付之卿身矣！吾亦無言可答，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>但有一句不敢說的話，不知尊前容納否？”宜人把臉一紅說：“何妨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>！”嫣娘起來，走到宜人身邊，低聲說道：“可嫌我否？”宜人把臉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一紅，斜著眼看了一眼，又笑了一笑。嫣娘深深作了一揖，就靠著宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人坐下，又低聲說：“此事吾當善謀之，卿可能徐待之？”宜人把臉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又一紅，把心一指說：“此處雖妾之靜室，然亦非相公久居之所。但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不知相公何處人？來此地何事？”嫣娘說：“我家在雨花台西邊。﹝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>現﹞在我是﹝到府﹞里赴考的，我父親也在這里。”宜人說：“你快</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些回去，看你父親找你。你若要再來，卻也不妨。”嫣娘聽他說父親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>找的話，就不敢再坐，站起來又依戀了一會，宜人扯著手，送他從一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小夾道到大門去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘到了寓處，正好他父﹝親﹞尚未回來。家人們問他：“到哪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里去了，叫俺們好找？”嫣娘支吾了一會，就躺在床上細細的想著宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人長的那個模樣，毋也息不了。不知後來如何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第五回  巧遇  重訪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘在床上躺著想著宜人，一時常興回來了。嫣娘只推身上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不快，常興只當是真的，又摸摸他的頭，就﹝說﹞：“頭倒不熱，只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>怕是多吃了東西了，你躺一時罷。”卻正合嫣娘之意，嫣娘又裝著哼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了兩聲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二天，嫣娘不敢仍然裝病，只得起來，又看看書，寫寫字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。過了一月，嫣娘總不得個空去宜人那里看看，心里卻時時在宜人身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上。又跟著院試近了，不免又忙著用了幾天功。常興又叫家人去辦場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>務、備卷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了考期、嫣娘進了場。到未初時候出來，甚是得意。常興接著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又問了他的文章可好，嫣娘不免公然自贊了一番。到第二日，放了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>榜，常興著家人去看，家人尚未回來，報子就報了，進了第二名。常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>興同嫣娘甚是歡喜。第二日又復試，至于獎賞送大人，一番應活是不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必說了。送了大人，常興就叫家人即時催了轎子，一齊回來。嫣娘實</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>打算可以再住幾日，偷著好去盼宜人一盼，哪知立時他父親就逼著回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了，嫣娘也只得飲恨吞聲而已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了家，常興又請了客。鄭氏也是歡喜，并娟、嫿、關、窈更是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>非常的歡喜是不必說了。只有嫣娘每日不惟不歡喜，反長吁短嘆的不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。娟、嫿、關、窈他們時常同他說笑，他不過勉強應酬而已。常興</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、鄭氏每每見他這樣，只當是在寓處的病未好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了八月下旬，雨花台臨近有一處禪院，名淨因庵。庵中桂花最</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>盛，又有幾處亭閣，最是幽雅。每年到桂花開時，游人如蟻。常興想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫嫣娘去敬敬。一日早晨，常興叫人到園里將嫣娘叫來。嫣娘來了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>常興說：“你天天在園里閑坐，何不今日到淨因庵去看看桂花？”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“好。我已經吃畢飯了，就去罷。”常興說：“叫個人跟著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“道不遠，何必要人跟著？”常興說：“你自己去也使得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，早早回來。”嫣娘答應著去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    出了門，果然去看花的不少。嫣娘也迤邐而去。到了庵內，看那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>佛殿前是五株大桂樹，上頭的枝葉把天都遮著了；又見幾處禪房小院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，也有幾株桂樹，或是丹如火，或是黃如金，各樣不一。那一種幽香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>真是沁人肺腑。嫣娘一處一處的看完了，又到一個客廳里坐下，和尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>捧了茶來。嫣娘吃了茶，和尚又擺上一桌小果碟子，嫣娘吃了幾樣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又吃了幾個點心。這是庵里的舊例，凡有人去游的皆如此待他，也不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是專為嫣娘而設。嫣娘吃完了，拿了隨帶的銀子一兩還了和尚。和尚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歡喜的了不得，眉開眼笑，又殷殷勤勤留住吃了茶，送了嫣娘出來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘出來，見天還早，看看離庵不遠，有一莊村，甚是幽靜，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>隨著步走了去。走到村前，看那小村外圍著一帶小溝，溝上有一小木</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>橋，溝內沿栽了有幾十本木芙蓉。嫣娘正在望那芙蓉，忽聽嘻嘻一陣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑聲。嫣娘仔細看去，才看著芙蓉花內隱隱約約有兩個人站在那里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘想道：“我何不從橋上踱過去？”就順著步一直過了橋。走到芙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>蓉花跟前，只聽上個人說：“姐姐，你看那個人跑進來了。”又聽一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個人說：“是誰？”嫣娘只得站在花下不敢一動，那兩個人一齊問道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“你來做甚么的？是想偷甚么？”嫣娘笑著說：“天下豈有賊秀才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>郎？”一個略高些的說：“我只當你是個賊，不知你是個秀才。你看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你的兩只眼東張西望的，可像個賊一樣？”嫣娘只是笑，也不敢出聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。那人又說：“你不實說你來做甚么，我就去喚狗來咬你。”說著就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要去。那個矮些個﹝的﹞說：“姐姐，你看他那個小樣，被姐姐罵了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一頓，怪可憐的，饒了他罷。”那人又向嫣娘著實的望了一眼，又微</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>微的笑了一笑，慢慢的小聲說：“暫且饒你這一次。”嫣娘就隔著花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>作了一個揖，說：“我是嫣娘，新進的秀才。”那高些的說：“秀才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是個甚么？是長的，是團的？是紅的，是綠的？”嫣娘說：“秀才不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是別的，是個功名。”那高些的說：“甚么叫個功名？”嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭上戴個頂兒，就叫功名。”那高些的說：“這個頂兒甚么稀罕的物</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>件，俺家放牛的小蝦兒天天把吃的雞蛋殼兒安在草帽上，豈不就是個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頂兒？”嫣娘說：“哪像個捐職的品頂戴，不是個秀才。”那高些的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你既然是個秀才，我問你，這株芙蓉花其種始于何時？來自何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>地？”嫣娘卻實在不知，又不好直說的，只是笑。那高些的說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>連這眼前的花木還不知道，也要戴個頂兒向人夸嘴說我是天下第一勝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>地南京首府秀才嫣娘，真真叫人不羞死也笑死了。”嫣娘聽了，又作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了一個揖，說：“小子請教。”那矮些的說：“姐姐，我們去罷，看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>那糊涂氣味熏壞了。”兩個說著就走。嫣娘站在路上攔住，笑著說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“才聽仙音，頓開茅塞，還望指教。”他兩個不得過去，說：“沒得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>指教了，你去罷！”嫣娘不肯閃開。他兩個動心了，那矮些的說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐姐，你把那芙蓉典賞給他聽聽罷。”那高些的沒了法，只說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>站遠一步，我跟你說。”嫣娘只得退了一步。那高些的說：“芙蓉出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>于日本國，周穆王好遠游三千，一年到了那國，攜來到中華的。你記</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，明日遇著學台考古，寫上就取個第一。”嫣娘說：“領教。”又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“豈有弟子不知師之名姓的？再懇把名姓賞給弟子聽聽。”那高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些的說：“你這個人不知好歹，怎么又問我們的名姓？”那矮些的說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“這又何妨？對他說就說。俺姓奚，姐姐叫引香，我叫拾香。你知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>道了，去罷。”嫣娘仍然不肯過去，不妨拾香把他一推，跌在地下，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他兩個跑了。嫣娘只得起來，慢慢回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了家，日日又添了一條牽挂，終日雖與娟、嫿、關、窈談談，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也不能解個悶。不覺又到了第二年秋天。這年就是秋闈之期。嫣娘到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了七月下旬就來府里等著入闈，又是常興送他，日日在寓不能出來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>那一日，常興要來家看鄉間田稞。嫣娘得了空，直跑到宜人門口，叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>開了門。進去有一條路，一直到宜人房里去的，他上回是宜人送他出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來走過的，所以他知道，就從這路一直到了宜人房里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    宜人在屋內小睡。嫣娘進了屋，﹝丫﹞頭就要叫醒宜人，嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“莫驚著他。”輕輕地走進屋，在靠床的一張兀凳上坐下，忽聽宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人夢里說：“一片情絲割不斷，有誰知？”將身一翻，眼朦朧著，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“好懶！”一眼看著床頭間一個人坐著，忙問說：“是誰？”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘小聲說：“是嫣娘。”宜人一翻身扒起來，想一把去拉嫣娘，又縮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>住了手說：“你怎么又來了？你怎么才來？”嫣娘說：“此心惟天可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>鑒！”說了這一句，那眼紅著，就說不出來了。宜人說：“好容易又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見一面，不說說話，哭甚么？”嫣娘說：“我這一個心，到哪一天才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見得我的真心？”宜人說：“你不用說，我都知道。”敘了一時，宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人又說：“我還有一個結拜的妹子，叫何粲。前日他聽我說，要等你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來，他來一顧。”嫣娘說：“嫣娘哪有這等福分，又得見一仙子。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人就叫丫頭往隔壁去請，一時阿粲來了。宜人出去接著，引著見了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘。嫣娘說：“才聞宜卿盛稱粲姐美德，相見之晚，實為恨事！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>阿粲說：“前得聞君子于宜姐，不勝欽仰！今日得見，信宜姐之言不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>虛矣。”宜人說：“你兩個不用客套了，吃茶罷。”叫丫頭捧上茶來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。吃了茶，宜人說：“粲妹的指法甚妙，何﹝不﹞來令君子一聆佳音</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”阿粲尚謙著說：“不善撫琴。”宜人給他代定了弦，按阿槳坐下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。阿槳只得撫弄了一會，是一曲《凰求鳳》。彈完了，嫣娘說：“不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>惟指法之妙，并此曲之意，亦妙不可言。”正在三個談話，阿粲家有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人來叫他，他就辭了他兩個去了。宜人說：“這妹子也是同我一樣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>出污泥而不染者。”嫣娘說：“佩服，佩服！”坐了一時，嫣娘又說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我今日本欲在此多坐一時，城中有一老師請用午飯，我暫去，明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日再來。”說著站起來就走。宜人送他到門首，他去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘一路走著，后邊來了一乘轎，從旁邊過去。嫣娘隔著小玻璃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窗子望著，真如嬌花初開，不知不覺就跟著轎去了。不知後來如何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第六回  假佣  真騙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘跟著轎去，那轎一直往三山街去了。嫣娘也跟到三山街</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，看著那轎到了一個大門，就抬進去了。嫣娘不敢進那大門，只得在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>門外站著，向內望了多時。回頭一看，這對門有個小茶肆。嫣娘把那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>老師請吃午飯的事早忘在九霄以外，看了這茶肆，就到肆里揀了一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小坐頭坐下，吃著茶，仍然目不轉睛的向那對門望著。忽然看見對門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>出來一個小廝，也到這茶肆里來吃茶，嫣娘想問問他，又不敢說。見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>那小廝進來，連忙讓他坐下。那小廝只當是認得他的，也就坐下了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說：“老兄尊姓？”小廝說：“姓胡。”嫣娘說：“我是這鄉間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人，才進城，想找個大人家去混碗飯吃，不知尊府里可能相容？”小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廝說：“暫時尚不等人用。等明年老爺回來，若果要人，我看尊兄甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>好，可以荐荐。”嫣娘說：“方才有一乘轎，是府中何人？”小廝說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“這是老太太房里的丫頭，叫個娉婷，今年十四歲了。方才是老太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>太叫他往寺里去替老太太拈香才回來。”嫣娘問到這里，也不敢再問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，只說：“現在府中既不要人，等明年我再來找老兄罷。”又吃了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>會茶，嫣娘算了茶帳，給了錢，與小廝拱拱手去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    走到寓處，才想起今日午間是老師請用飯，天卻已到申時了，只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>得推個病，叫家人去給老師請安，稟明了不能來領飯的話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    又過了幾天，常興來了，場期也到了。常興叫家人諸事替他辦齊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。嫣娘進了頭場、二場、三場，場畢將文章、詩策、經文俱已騰出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>稿來。常興拿著去請素日相識的親友看看，個個都是稱贊。常興歡喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，就同嫣娘在府候榜。過了幾日，揭了曉，報子報了，中了解元。常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>興、嫣娘自是歡喜不必說了，至于赴鹿鳴宴、拜老師這一番的事也不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必說了。諸事完了，常興同嫣娘回來，到了家，自然又是唱戲請客，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也不必說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    家中事畢。嫣娘閑著，又同娟、嫿、關、窈一處頑笑。娟姐說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“你如今是老爺了，我們還稱你相公不成？”嫣娘說：“老爺倒是老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>爺，只是老爺這個混名，寫在題名錄上未免不雅。”又說：“你們這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些人真真是天天作夢，還不知道我去考的時候，就起了大名叫常敏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我進學就是這個名字，中舉也是這個名子。”關關說：“甚么敏不敏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？我說沒有嫣娘兩個字，念的嘴里也好，聽的耳朵里也好。”窈窈說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“一個人自然有個大名，有個乳名，豈可把乳名當了大名？”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“莫說這名字的話了。我問你們，我如今是老爺，你們是甚么呢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”娟姐說：“我們四個還是丫頭。”嫣娘說：“你們既然還是丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，我自己一個做個老爺有甚么趣？不如我叫你們也叫老爺罷！”引的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大家都笑起來。嫿姐說：“你這些小孩子的話，到哪一天才不說了？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    正在說話，一個丫頭來說：“相公快些上去，爺一下跌倒不說話</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”嫣娘連忙跑到上房，常興已經閉著眼發喘。鄭氏守著哭，見嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘來了，鄭氏說：“你快些叫你父親！”嫣娘叫了一聲，常興把眼微</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>微一睜，把頭略略一點，就嗚呼了。嫣娘嚎啕大慟。鄭氏忙著叫家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>備了后事。俱已全了，將柩停在中堂。鄭氏想家中無人照料，把當典</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里一個老伙計請來做了朝奉，凡家中事一一交他照料。這伙計姓李，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>名立，本是在常家典里多年的人，亦老成，受了鄭氏的囑托，就將常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>興的喪事不丰不儉的辦完了。又擇了本莊的吉地，到七七上葬了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘在家守制，外邊有李立管理家務，仍然是自由自在的。過了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>半年，因在制不好出門，就想著：“家中無事，何不將這花園從新修</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>造修造？”又想：“這園如何修法才好？”想了一時，忽然想起那年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在畫箱里見了一個西洋園圖，何不就照那樣去修？遂去將畫箱開了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>找了圖出來，鋪在桌上細細看去。看著第一層是個大門，進了大門是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個月門，當著門是個六方亭子，四外俱是小紅闌干，亭子上俱滿裝格</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子。這個亭子是要連著正庭的意思，亭子外即一長池，池上一水橋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>橋上兩旁俱是小闌干。過了橋是正庭，過了正庭，庭后是一大假山，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大假山兩旁是兩小假山。大假山正中一洞門，門上鐫著三個字，是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“等閑鄉”，左邊小假山的洞門上鐫著是：“處處”，右邊小假山的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>洞門上鐫著是：“所所”。這三個門，原進去是三個園，正中是大園</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，兩旁是小園，俱是假山遮斷，兩小園假山空里，又各有小夾道通著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是園。嫣娘看畢，拍手大笑，說：“妙地，妙地！我就照著這樣去修</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，并園名亦照著這樣。”就叫家人向李立說，叫了匠人動工，把娟、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫿、關、窈俱以挪出到上邊廂房去住。又派了幾個能干的家人，把圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>交給他，叫他照樣去修。家人領著匠人天天去修。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘想，宜人哪里是知道我的，我守制不好去的，就是引香、拾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香，這也太近了，一則不好去，二則去也未必得見，不如去訪訪娉婷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。嫣娘就向鄭氏說：“我想到外面去逛逛，不過臨近幾家，不幾日就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>回來。”鄭氏說：“也好。家里雖然修理，有家人照應，且有李朝奉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在家，諸事可以問他，你去也罷。”嫣娘就換下重孝服，穿了素服出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一直到了三山街，又到那茶肆里找著那胡小廝。那胡小廝見了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“老兄來了，怎么穿著素服？”嫣娘說：“我如今大總的沒依靠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，我老人家又沒了，我想求求老兄，替我引進引進。”小廝說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>老兄來的甚好，我家老爺才回來。內花園的書房沒人照看，正要尋人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。像老兄這干干淨淨的，且年輕又伶俐，老爺看著是必收的。”說著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，就起來說：“你同我到那邊去。”嫣娘就跟著他到了大門。進了門</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，到了門房里，管門的家人問說：“這是哪個？”小廝說：“這是我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的朋友，也要來我們家來的。”又向嫣娘說：“這是張二爺。”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就給他作了一揖。管門的叫他坐下，小廝說：“老兄坐著，我進去回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺。”小廝去了，一時來了，說：“老兄快來！老爺在內書房，我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>引你進去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    小廝引著嫣娘進了二門，又進了穿庭、大庭、茶庭。從茶庭院西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一小角門，進了角門一條長夾道，夾道頭前又一小門，進了門往左一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>轉，就是內宅的角門；往右一轉，就是個小花園。進了花園，嫣娘看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這花園雖不甚大，卻也精致。幾處小假山，后頭俱玲玲瓏瓏；幾株松</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>樹、梅樹、梧桐樹，也是古古致致；又有幾株湘妃竹，疏疏落落。小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廝引著進了書房。嫣娘看這書房是四間，中間設著大羅汗榻，兩旁俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是博古圖書架，架上設著各樣古董玩意。頭間有一碧紗櫥，小廝引著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>進了櫥子，嫣娘看窗前一幾，幾上設著筆硯等物；上邊有一小榻，榻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上盤膝坐著一個五十許的人。小廝說：“給老爺叩頭。”嫣娘只得磕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了兩個頭。那老爺說：“起來罷。”嫣娘起來站在旁邊，那老爺看了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一看，說：“你可識字？”嫣娘說：“小的識字。”那老爺說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就在這里伺候罷。”嫣娘答應著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    過了三日，那老爺因在任之事未清，有文書提他，他就連忙去了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，將內書房交給嫣娘照應。嫣娘就天天掐花送于老太太房里插瓶，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>掐些送送各處丫頭們。混了幾天混熟了，見了妯婷，也時常說一句兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>句話。一天，老太太叫娉婷到園內去，看可有新開的花掐幾枝來。娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了園，只聽書房里一個人在那里哼哼唧唧，像念書的樣。娉婷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>想道：“這是誰？”偷偷到窗跟前，隔著紗看去，只見嫣娘在那里背</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著手，念那壁上懸的詩屏。娉婷在外叫著說：“你這個小廝，瘋了不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>成？在那里哼什么？”嫣娘聽是娉婷說話，就連忙說：“請姐姐到屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里坐。”娉婷說：“我不進去。”嫣娘說：“這有何妨？”說著嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就出來了，到了廊下，娉婷也到了廊下。嫣娘說：“姐姐今年十幾？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去年秋天坐轎從哪里來？”娉婷說：“你這個人說話真是奇怪，我今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>年十幾，與你甚么相干？我去年坐轎，你怎么知道？”嫣娘聽了，“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>噯喲”了一聲，說：“我今個可有死的地方了。”娉婷說：“你莫當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>真的瘋了？”嫣娘說：“不瘋，不瘋！真真是真話。”娉婷說：“怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么是真話？”嫣娘說：“一言難盡，我也無從說起。”娉婷說：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>站乏了，我進屋里來，我們坐下。我倒要聽你細細的說說。”娉婷進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了屋，到榻上坐下，嫣娘也到下邊椅子坐下。娉婷說：“你說。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“你可知道我是個什么人？”娉婷說：“你是個小廝。”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“像我這個小廝，這南京三年才出一個。”娉婷說：“怎么這等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>稀罕？”嫣娘說：“我是去年的新解元常敏。”娉婷說：“你真瘋了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，豈有解元情願給人家做小廝的？”嫣娘說：“我是來救你的。”娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷說：“我又無病無災，要你救甚么？”嫣娘說：“我自從去年秋天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在轎里見過你，我想你這樣一個人，可惜，可惜！”娉婷說：“怎么</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>可惜？”嫣娘說：“你想，你想。”娉婷把臉一紅，說：“你這個人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還了得嗎？我去向老太太說，打不死你！”說著就走。嫣娘說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去只管去，你想我這話到底是為誰？”娉婷站了一時，說：“我去看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>老太太，等我改日再說罷。”不知后來怎樣說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第七回  花歸  珠還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說娉婷說著怕老太太等他，就出來到院子里，隨手掐了兩枝花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去了。將花送于老太太看了，老太太叫他把窗前幾上一個白磁大瓶灌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上水，將花插上。娉婷去灌了水，雙手捧著，一路走來，心里卻想著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘的話，走到堂階上，一步未上完，手中的就“滑郎”一聲，在石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭上成了白玉開花了。娉婷就嚇呆了站在那里。老太太聽著，罵了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頓，又說：“你這小蹄子不中用，明日拉出去配個小廝就完了。”娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷站了一時，也不敢再來見老太太，就到下邊廂房坐著去了。坐在窗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>下一張椅子上，一邊靠著桌子，手托著腮，噙著眼淚想著：“我自小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>到這里，從沒受過這樣的氣，沒想到老太太說拉出去配小廝的話。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>想了一會，“這真真是園里那人說的話，說我可惜可惜了。”越想越</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>酸心，不覺嗚嗚咽咽哭了一場。到了晚上，老太太著人叫了去，又數</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說了一頓，說：“我說你幾句，你就使性子不來了？”娉婷又站了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>時，老太太說：“你必然歇罷？明日一早還到園里去看，有新開的花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>再掐幾枝來，我那案頭上還有一個翡翠瓶，你沒摔完，好再來摔這個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，去罷。”娉婷去了，到了廂房，和衣睡下，左思右想沒個結局。想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>今日這個沒趣，不過是老太太一時生氣，后來自然仍是一樣，那配小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廝的話，畢竟這一輩子難免了。一直哭到天亮，又不敢不去掐花，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>早早起來，也未裝束，就去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了園，看嫣娘正在那里澆花。嫣娘見娉婷來了，就笑嘻嘻的說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“姐姐怎么起來鎮早？”娉婷也不理他，嫣娘又說：“怎么姐姐也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不梳頭，就衣冠不整下堂來了？”娉婷仍是不理他。嫣娘看娉婷站在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>那里，問他話他不說，又不是掐花，呆呆站著。嫣娘說：“姐姐好像</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>受了委屈的樣？”娉婷仍是不理他。嫣娘嘆了一口氣，說：“噯，可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>惜，可惜！”娉婷說：“怎么可惜？”嫣娘說：“姐姐是聰明人，這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>‘可惜’二字還來問我？我是個局外人，這‘可惜’中的甘苦只怕還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>知之不真，姐姐在‘可惜’局中的，這甘苦自然是都領略過了。”娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷聽了，不覺將身一蹲，蹲在地上放聲大哭。嫣娘連忙問說：“姐姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，這是何必？”連忙又作了一個揖，說：“是我的不是，一時言語沖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著了。”又說：“這清早地下濕氣甚厲害，蹲在這里受了寒也不是頑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的。”娉婷拭拭眼淚，就站起來一直往書房里去，嫣娘也跟進來。娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷說：“你來﹝做甚﹞么？”嫣娘說：“不是姐姐叫我嗎？”娉婷說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我何曾叫你？”嫣娘說：“姐姐來園里來，自然是掐花，為何到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>書房里來？難道這書房里栽花不成？”娉婷說：“人心里過不得，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還嘔人！”嫣娘說：“我雖不才，姐姐如果有甚煩惱，我也可以分分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>懮，何不說說？”娉婷說：“我對你說也是無益。”嫣娘說：“或者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有益，亦未可知。”娉婷叫嫣娘站近些，就小聲把昨日的事一一告于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他。嫣娘把眼一紅，就淌下眼淚來了。娉婷替他拭了一拭，說：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>問你可有甚么法，你只是哭，終有何益？”嫣娘說：“姐姐坐下，等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我想想。”娉婷就坐下了，又叫嫣娘也靠近坐下。嫣娘說：“姐姐何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不將計就計？”娉婷說：“怎么將計就計？”嫣娘說：“姐姐只管仍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>然不做錯這就做錯那，或者仍然與老太太嘔氣，或者天天偷空就去睡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，或者再是老太太罵你，你就裝著尋死。”嫣娘說一句，娉婷把頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>點一點。娉婷說：“到后來到底怎么樣？”嫣娘說：“只等老太太氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你不過，要打發你了，我就回去著人來買你，到我家去服侍我母親。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐姐后來，我自然有個安排。”娉婷說：“你幾時回去？”嫣娘說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“我等姐姐有信，就給他做個金蟬脫殼之計。”娉婷又點點頭。嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“姐姐去罷。看老太太怪你。姐姐以后也莫來了，看旁人疑惑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”說著，嫣娘就到院子里替娉婷掐了幾枝花，交給娉婷拿著去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娉婷果然從了嫣娘的計，天天嘔氣，嘔了十幾天。老太太始而罵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他，繼而勸他，他總是不改，老太太氣著叫家人來說要打發他，這也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是個氣話，原是嚇他的意思。誰知他仍然不改，并且時常偷著要上吊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，要吃毒藥，老太太怕將來鬧的不好，就當真要打發他了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娉婷一聞此信，這日就起個早，走到園門口叫嫣娘說：“解元回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去罷！”說完了，連忙跑了，嫣娘從書房里出來就不見他了。嫣娘知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是其計已成，就到大門首找著胡小廝，拉到對門茶肆里坐下，吃了兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>碗茶，嫣娘說：“我承老兄照看，這有一個財，想叫老兄發發，以為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>謝禮，不知可受不受？”胡小廝笑著說：“甚么財照顧小弟？”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我聽府里要打發丫頭，不知是哪個？人才如何？年紀多大？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>胡小廝說：“是老太太房里的，老兄是去年在轎里看過的。”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我有個表兄，姓李，要買人，老兄若能去說，包管謝儀加厚。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>胡小廝喜歡的了不得，就一口應承說：“在我，在我。”嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這還等我回去，先向他說明才好。”胡小廝說：“老兄只管去，園中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的事我替你照應。”嫣娘就去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了家，見堂屋院里放著些桌椅并米面等物，嫣娘也未及問就進</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了堂屋。見了鄭氏，鄭氏問他在哪里住了一兩個月，嫣娘就隨口支吾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“不是在一家。”隨口編了幾家。鄭氏說：“怪道我著人去找你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，再找不著。”嫣娘說：“不是還未得回來，只因有一家有個丫頭要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>賣，我想俺家人甚少，母親何不叫李朝奉去買來。”鄭氏最是疼兒子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的，豈有不肯的，就說：“你去向李朝奉說就是了。”嫣娘出來，見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了李立說：“三山街有個許老爺家，他家有個丫頭，奶奶要買，你去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>帶二三百銀子，找著他家家人姓胡的，說有個王貴向我說你家府里有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個丫頭要賣，我是來買的，不拘多少銀子，務必買來。外謝姓胡的二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>十兩銀子，就說這謝儀也是王貴說明的。他若要問王貴，你就認作是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你表弟，說他不幾日就來。在我家替我照料事。”李立說：“買丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這事容易，又是什么王貴，我不懂。”嫣娘就發了急說：“你真真罷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了！連這點頭小事也不能辦，你只管去像我這樣說就是了。”李立也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不敢再問，只得拿著銀子去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘又到堂屋，見了鄭氏，說明李立去了，又問說：“院子放這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些東西做甚么？”鄭氏說：“你還不知道，李朝奉有個姐姐在這不遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>住，他姐丈姓奚。前日午后被禍了，一家可憐燒了個干淨，只有他姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>丈、姐姐并他兩個甥女單人跑出來。李朝奉來求了我，將這左邊空房</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>賃去暫住，又把他兩個甥女叫引香、拾香﹝的﹞結義于我做了干女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這些東西是送給他們的，你問著也去看看。”嫣娘連忙答應著，又說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“人家有難，母親該重重的周濟周濟，這太少了。”鄭氏說：“等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>明日再送。”嫣娘說完了話，就到廂房里來，與娟、嫿、關、窈談談</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又說起如今你們好了，又來個伴了，娟、嫿、關、窈又問了一會這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些時在那里的話，嫣娘也是隨嘴答應了幾句，又出來去看看園子修理</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的如何，又想就去看引香、拾香，又怕他們不理應著，不如等老李來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>同他一齊去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    天到了傍晚時候，見李立引著一乘小轎進來了。下了轎，嫣娘看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著是娉婷，卻閃在一邊，讓李立去叫了丫頭來引他進去。娉婷跟著丫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭進了大庭、茶庭、宅門，到了堂屋見了鄭氏，給鄭氏磕了頭。娉婷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>四下一望，卻不見嫣娘，心里到著了忙了，想道：“那小廝莫不是個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>解元，怎么他家也這樣富貴？”又想道：“這莫不是他家，那小廝莫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是個拐子？”又想：“若是拐子，怎么肯用一二百銀子買我？”狐疑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不定，站了一時。鄭氏叫了丫頭送他到廂房同娟、嫿、關、窈一處去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。娉婷跟著丫頭到了廂房，娟、嫿、關、窈接著，互施了禮坐下。娟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、嫿四個人看這娉婷眉如遠黛，目會秋波，腮點桃花，腰同細柳，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>四個心里不勝羨慕。娉婷就問了他四個的年紀并各人的名字，他四個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又問了他的年紀名字。娟姐說：“娉姐在舊主人處甚好，何故又到這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里來？”娉婷不好說的，只是含糊答應。忽見嫣娘進來，娉婷見了低</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭一笑，也不站起來。娟姐說：“這是小主人相公。”娉婷又笑了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑，嫣娘也笑了一笑。娟、嫿、關、竊他四個到你望著我，我望著你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，不勝詫異。娉婷說：“解元是今日哪個時候來家的？”嫣娘也不答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>應，只笑了一笑。娟、嫿、關、窈心里倒疑惑他怎么知道他是解元，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娉婷又說：“我蒙解元之德，何以為報？”嫣娘說：“你想著怎么報</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就是怎么報。”他兩個說話，娟、嫿四個越聽越糊涂，娉婷又說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我來也罷了，只是老太太跟前，我孝敬了這幾年，把老太太的恩也算</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>報了個萬分之一。只是我家小姐并小姐之婢我那妹子，一時離了未免</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫人傷感。”嫣娘聽到這里，卻忘了把做小廝的事瞞著娟、嫿四個，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就問道：“我在書房住了這幾﹝日﹞，怎么未見過小姐并你那妹子？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”娉婷還未答應，嫿姐說：“相公跟他舊主人有親嗎？往他家去做甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么？你到他家是個客，他家天天有人陪著他家小姐，知道外邊有客，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>豈肯進來的呢？”嫣娘說：“不是去作客。”嫿姐說：“不是去作客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，到他家作甚么？”嫣娘說：“你問娉姐就知道了。”娉婷說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>莫叫嫿姐問我，我不知道。”嫣娘說：“這個話等我晚上來睡時閑著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>再說，你們也不必問了。”又向娟、嫿四個人說：“娉姐來的是客，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你們凡床帳這些照應照應，我出去有事。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘出來，找著李立，問明了買娉婷的事，又挾他說：“我母親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>把你兩個甥女作了干女，我們是干姐妹了，我去看看，且看看你令姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、姐丈。”李立說：“我姐丈出門去了，你要去，我同你去。”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就同李立去了。到了奚家，先見了李立之姐，嫣娘也稱個伯母；又請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見了引香、拾香。坐下敘了一時話，引香想道這個人好像見過的，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不好問嫣娘。嫣娘因他母親在跟前，也不敢問引香、拾香的。一時嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘去了，引香向拾香說：“這個人妹妹可曾見過他？”拾香說：“好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>像那年秋天那個不知芙蓉典的秀才。”引香說：“聽說這是解元。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>拾香說：“解元原是秀才中的，焉知不是他？”正在猜疑，忽見來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一個丫頭向他母親說：“俺家奶奶給奚奶奶請安。俺家奶奶說明日請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個小姐搬在俺那邊去住，俺家相公與這里小姐也皇干姐妹了。相公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的性情極好，常在一處談談也不妨的。”李氏說：“你回去給奶奶請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>安，說我方才也見了你家相公了，引香、拾香也見了相公了。我看你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>家相公甚好，明日就叫他兩個搬去。”丫頭去了。這原是嫣娘回來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見了鄭氏說：“母親沒人作伴，何不將奚家姊妹接來？”鄭氏原也喜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歡引香、拾香，所以著人來接。不知搬來沒搬來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         第八回  遞書  泣賣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說李氏許了那丫頭，說叫引香、拾香搬來。到了第二天，果然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>李氏就將引香、拾香送過來了。見了鄭氏，敘了一時。李氏要走，鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏又留住吃了午飯才去，李氏去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    鄭氏叫人將東廂房收拾了給引香、拾香住下。引香、拾香到了東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廂房。這房子對面就是西廂房，是娟、嫿、關、窈、娉婷五個人住的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。一時嫣娘來了，到堂屋見了鄭氏，鄭氏說：“你見過你干姊妹沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”嫣娘說：“昨日是母親叫去看看，我去了。今日還未見他。”鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏就叫丫頭到東廂房去請兩個奚小姐來。一時引香、拾香來了，與嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘施了禮坐下。鄭氏說：“你們這是姊妹了，不可不分個長幼。”就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>問了引香、拾香的年紀，卻是引香長嫣娘一歲，拾香小嫣娘一歲。鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏向嫣娘說：“你以后就叫引姐姐，拾妹妹就是了。”又向引香、拾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香說：“你兩個以后就叫嫣娘哥哥、弟弟就是了。天天在一塊，總要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>和氣些，莫生疏了。”嫣娘、引香、拾香俱站起來答應著。鄭氏又說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“嫣娘，你去送姐姐、妹妹到東廂房里去看看，看可少甚么東西，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>照應照應。”嫣娘答應著，同引香、拾香去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了東廂房，一齊坐下，引香說：“弟弟，你可怪我。”嫣娘笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著說：“沒甚怪的。”引香說：“你不記得那年在芙蓉花下我搶白了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你一頓。”嫣娘說：“姐姐的話我怎敢忘，我正是心悅誠服不了，哪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>還有怪的意思？”拾香說：“哥哥不怪我姐姐，我把你推在地下，自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>然是怪我的了。”嫣娘笑了一笑說：“這更是不怪，若不是妹妹一推</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，只怕到如今我還在那里站著哩！”正在說話，丫頭拿了一封書進來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“這是前邊李朝奉說有人送來給相公的。”嫣娘接過來一看，上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>面紅阡上寫著：“解元常君手啟”。嫣娘想道這必是宜人的書子，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>折開，背過臉來偷著去看。看了一回，把眼紅著，幾乎掉下淚來。引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香問說：“甚么人送來的，又是甚么事這樣張皇？”說著就要來看書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子，嫣娘把書子往袖中一籠說：“姐姐看他怎么？”一句未說完，哪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>知書子未曾籠好，把袖子一拂就掉下來了。拾香在旁趁勢搶去，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>想來奪，拾香已經拿跑了。嫣娘說：“這個書子我原想給姐姐、妹妹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>看的，替我想個主意。救人一命，也是姐姐、妹妹的修行。”引香說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“這書子到是甚么事？”嫣娘要說還未說，拾香說：“等我念給你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聽。”嫣娘說：“好妹子，小聲些！”拾香點點頭，就小聲念道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    昔勞春注辱臨蝸廬，去后神思，又蒙仙風一度，洵為幸幸。今越</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>載未親芝范，易勝惆悵之至。愚意以為暫時小別，終當聚首。不料變</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>生不測，家慈有亦珠之意。再抱琵琶，赧顏殊甚，決不敢負前日之德</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，而貽君子之羞也。阿粲小妹同出一轍。望早援手，是切，是禱！宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人襝衽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    拾香念完了，嫣娘說：“請二位高明指示指示。”引香說：“這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有何難，費幾兩銀子就完了。”拾香說：“姐姐之見與我相同。這個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人我想必是個才貌雙全的，來跟我們在一塊，豈不又得個良友？”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘笑著說：“我說他，你們也不信，等來個就知道了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘就出來找著李立，向李立說：“河坊有個姓何的、姓翁的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他兩家有個小女要賣，一個叫宜人，一個叫阿粲，你去買來，難為難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>為！”李立說：“奶奶不知道，我怎么敢去？”嫣娘說：“我一時去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說就是了，你莫耽擱了，快去罷！我明日好好備個菜請請你。”李立</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑著去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘只望一時就來才好，急的了不得，只得又往園里去看看，借</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著散散悶。到了天晚，李立來了。嫣娘看李立自己一個來了，就慌了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，忙問說：“怎么你自己來了？必是人家已經賣了，不是就是你舍不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>得多出錢？”李立說：“事成了。我對你說，我一去，他家聽說是你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>家買，就要幾千銀子。后來我哄他，我說是我買了做妾。”嫣娘說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“你這話該死該死，你死了定要下拔舌頭的地獄。”李立說：“這樣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說不好，莫買就是了。”嫣娘又笑著說：“好人，你對我說罷，到底</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>怎生了？”李立說：“我說是我買也花了幾百銀子，何家的是二百八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>十兩，翁家的是二百七十兩，說明了明日去接。”嫣娘歡喜不了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說宜人聽著說將他賣于一個姓李的，年紀有五十多歲，阿粲也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是賣給他，宜人就大哭了一會。哭完了，就著人去請了阿粲來，又同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>哭了一會，宜人說：“哭也算不了我們的事，想俺兩個見嫣娘的時候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>俱是彈琴，我想我作個《清商怨》，你彈著，我唱，發抒發抒這一腔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的幽恨，何如？”阿粲說：“好。”就理了弦彈著，彈出那一段如泣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如訴的音來，宜人這邊唱道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    這孤燈影醉，坐著俺兩個人兒，一遞一聲長嘆。嘆的是有緣的偏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>無緣，嘆的是無緣的反有緣，嘆的是好因緣變成了惡因緣。恨只恨前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>生不曾見，恨只恨今生見了如不見，恨只恨來生不知可能再相見。俺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個人兒，你對著我，我對著你，悽悽慘慘，嗚嗚咽咽。可憐俺買風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>光錯使了金錢，可憐俺種美玉錯耕了藍田，可憐俺訪桃源錯上了漁船</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。只想著見那月下老兒，罵他一番，為甚么把紅繩不緊緊的手牽？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    唱畢了，琴聲猶悠悠揚揚未斷，忽聽窗外烏鴉戛然一聲，看著外</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>邊月明如畫，阿粲向宜人說：“姐姐何不打開窗子向外一望，憑我兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個人的眼望斷子淯波森森，就是嫣娘不來，也算我們不辜他了。”宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人同何粲開了窗子向外望著，宜人用手指著向阿粲說：“這就是嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>那年坐船從這里來的。”阿粲說：“水呵，水呵，你也太無情了，為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何前日送人來，今日就不送人來了？”宜人又指著這窗前說：“嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就是從這里上來的。”阿粲說：“窗子呵，你也太不知事了，為何人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了你就不曾留住？”又聽著烏鴉叫了一聲，宜人說：“烏鴉，你何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必這樣太狠，一聲一聲的，把我的心都叫碎了。”阿粲說：“這烏鴉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>想必也是可憐我們兩個，前來一助悲聲的，不然就是這烏鴉也或者是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>情有所鐘不能自禁了。”宜人說：“關了窗子罷。我這時甚渴，叫丫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭烹茶吃罷。”阿粲說：“想必是心火上炎，我亦如是。”他兩個就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>坐了一夜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二天，嫣娘一早就催李立來接。李立帶銀子來交明了，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雇了兩乘小轎，李立引著來了。到了大門，進來到了大庭，下了轎，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>進了茶庭。宜人、阿粲見嫣娘站在屋里，宜人就哭著說：“你怎么也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在這里，可能救救我兩個？”阿粲也是哭。嫣娘連忙說：“你兩個到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上頭去，我就來。”宜人說：“噯！真真天下男子最是薄情，天下女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子最是痴情！我兩個待你不薄，如今我們到這個地位，你不替我們解</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>解懮，還要得空就跑，翻然不顧，是何心腸？”阿粲說：“姐姐說他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>怎么，他既是沒個人心的人，怨我們當初瞎了眼睛，如今還說甚么了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”他兩個說著，哭著，嫣娘急的紅脹了臉，也說不出話來了。一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>丫頭出來將他兩個引進去，他兩個拭了拭眼淚，見了鄭氏，磕了頭，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我們都是下賤人，奶奶何必叫爺要我們？”鄭氏不懂，只道是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說嫣娘，鄭氏說：“我聽嫣娘說，你們都是有難的人，他買你們來是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>救你們的，怎么說下賤不下賤？”宜人想道這其中必有緣故，就說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“不是說下賤，是求奶奶可憐可憐的意思。”鄭氏說：“你兩個到西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廂房同你姊妹們去坐坐罷。”一時嫣娘來了，到了西廂見了宜、粲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人說：“你到底做甚么鬼，叫俺兩個也不明白？”嫣娘說：“我還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>未說清，你兩個就哭起來了，叫我急的沒法，大總說不上來了。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘才從頭把李立之事說清，大家歡喜不了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘就日日催著家人，叫匠人上緊修理。又過了一個月，園修起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。嫣娘又叫李立去叫家人將各處所用幾榻桌椅等物送進園去，又叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>李立叫家人將各處所栽花木并所養的仙鶴、孔雀、鸚哥、八哥等鳥俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>以買全送進園去。嫣娘就向鄭氏說：“園修起了，我想搬進去住。這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>園原是一園而分三園，三園而合一園，我在當中大園名‘等閑鄉’的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>住，可以叫奚家姐姐、妹妹到左邊處去住，若是嫌沒人作伴，就叫宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人、阿粲去陪他。右邊留著閑逛。”鄭氏允了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    擇了日子一齊搬進去，嫣娘引著引香、拾香、宜人、阿粲、娉婷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>并娟、嫿、關、窈，先從大門進去，由亭子過小橋，過花庭，到了“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>等閑鄉”這洞門，嫣娘說：“這正中就是我住的。”又望著引香、拾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香說：“這左邊是姐姐、妹妹住的。”引香、拾香就要從那里進去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說：“不必。就從這正中走，中間里邊也有路可通。”就一齊從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>正中進去，見左一假山，右一花障，曲曲彎彎，無非幽境，又有高高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>迴迴隨著地勢蓋的亭子，小齋有十幾處。到了正房，是五間，正中是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>三間，兩邊各有碧紗櫥，櫥內一間。一齊坐下，又看了看屋內的陳設</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。一時引香說：“我們也到我們的住處去看看。”引香同著拾香、宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人、﹝阿粲﹞去了，嫣娘又叫娟、嫿、關、窈送去，一齊都去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘問娉婷說：“你前日說你家小姐，我也不得問你，這人品如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何，何不向我說說？”娉婷把身子一扭，說：“可笑，可笑！”不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娉婷說不說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第九回  訴情  探病</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說娉婷說嫣娘可笑，嫣娘說：“這不過是我仰止之意，有甚可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑的？”娉婷說：“我常聽他們說小說的每每總是有個佳人，來了個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>才子，這才子與佳人就你貪我愛，其中總是個丫頭作線索，即如《西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廂》的曲子，依我看來，雖是鶯鶯不該出來閑游遇見了張生，老夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不該遇兵圍寺，急中不暇深思將鶯鶯許了張生，評論《西廂》的人都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歸罪于老夫人、鶯鶯，我則說這罪全是紅娘的。”嫣娘說：“這個高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>論，我卻未之前聞，願領教而受業于門。”娉婷說：“你想起初張生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見了紅娘，張生的一番言語，若是紅娘是個知禮知義的人，把張生之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>言置若罔聞，不向鶯鶯去說，哪有這后來一段公案？我知道張生以為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>無望，他也必趁早去了，你以我的此番話為何如？”嫣娘說：“敬服</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，敬服。”娉婷笑了一笑說：“我看我那小姐將來也必是個有福的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“你何以知之？”娉婷說：“小姐的容貌也形容不盡，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是他這名子叫富春，可謂名稱其實了。就是我那妹子叫雁奴的，也可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在美人中不數第二。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    正在說著，娟、嫿、關、窈來了。嫣娘怕他四個問方才的話，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>四個一進來，嫣娘就向他們說：“明日是九月九了，我們到園里來還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來賞賞這園子，明日可以在這高處的亭然亭上登高，你們大家想想明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日怎么頑法，明日你五個不拘誰早些，去請處處的四位來。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二天一早，引香、拾香、宜人、阿粲俱來了，嫣娘知道是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>已經請了，就在這正房里吃了早飯，就到亭然亭上去了。大家坐了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>時，又各各遠眺了一會，引香說：“想我們這些人，雖不敢當‘紅顏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>’二字，而‘薄命’二字依我看去，卻是個個當成了。我想我家雖不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>甚富而凍餒無懮，也可自足，偏偏為火所妒，如今寄人宇下，真是比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>王摩詰‘獨在異鄉為異客’那個登高的更是難受了。”說著長嘆了幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聲。宜人說：“要論我與阿粲妹子之苦，更是走到蜜州也是苦的了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”娉婷說：“我如今雖然比前略可心安些，然大海茫茫何日到岸？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娟姐說：“我是揚州人，可憐到這里孤孤單單，也實在難受。”嫿姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我雖是本處人，自小父母兄弟俱無，誰更有比我還苦些的？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關關說：“我是蘇州人，跟這窈窈妹子住的相離不遠，從小在一塊頑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，可憐后來都是少父無母的，不料如今卻又在一處，這倒是幸？是不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>幸？我也不知道了。”大家正在各說各的事，拾香回過頭來看著嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在那里拭眼淚，拾香說：“像你這樣還有甚么不足的？從小父母愛如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>掌上之珠，后來年輕輕的就進了學，中了解元，家里又如此富足，雖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是干父不在了，人之修短有數，這也是他老人家的大限如此。”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我哭的不是這些，哭的是我聽你們這些話太聽遲了。”拾香說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“旁人都在傷心，你這個傷心又是傷心之外的傷心了。”說著丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>將登高的果子菜肴四五十個小西洋碟子都捧上來放在亭子上，眾人一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>齊坐下，吃了一會酒，嫣娘說：“我常聽人家結義拜弟兄，我們何不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>敘敘齒，也修個蘭譜”。嫣娘就問了，是引香大些，其次是娟姐，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>其次是娉婷，嫿姐、宜人都是與他同歲的，嫿姐大他兩個月，宜人小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他十幾天，再其次就是拾香、阿粲、關關、窈窈，嫣娘在第五。嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你們以后都叫我五娘罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一時酒吃畢了，都下來到正房坐下，嫣娘說：“我這個敝廬未有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>堂名，請引姐姐賜一小額。”引香說：“可以叫個明月清風廬。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“甚好，甚好！”引香說：“你也替我起個堂名擱在我的住處</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”嫣娘說：“叫個‘妙居’可好？”引香說：“不敢當，我用個‘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聊寄齋’罷。”嫣娘說：“姐姐未免太多心了。”又坐了一時，引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、拾香、宜人、阿粲都去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二日一早，宜人來向嫣娘說：“引香小姐昨日回去，想是午間</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在亭子上受了風了，夜間發熱病了，你去看看，或者著人去請個郎中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來調治調治。”嫣娘聽了，連忙同著宜人到了聊寄齋，宜人說：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有事不得陪你，你自己進去罷。”嫣娘進了里間屋，看引香在床上躺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，拾香在床沿上坐著，阿粲在那里烹茶。嫣娘走到床沿上，靠近拾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香坐下，問引香說：“姐姐覺心里如何？”引香說：“沒大病，不過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>略略受寒而已。”嫣娘說：“姐姐莫外人氣，要吃甚么對我說，要喝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>什么對我說，要頑個甚么頑意解解悶也對我說說。”說著又去摸摸引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香的頭，說：“覺有些汗意，莫要動，這汗出了就好了。”嫣娘同引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香說話，拾香因要拿茶葉出去了，阿粲去叫丫頭們拿水，也去了。嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“姐姐好好養著，等明日好了，到下雪的時候，我們好好賞雪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”又說：“姐姐，我在這里說話你可心煩？”引香向他說：“難得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>難得，你去罷。”嫣娘站起來就要走，引香說：“我還跟你說話。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘又站住，引香卻沒的說，微微一笑說：“去罷。”嫣娘說：“他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們還未來，我去沒人給姐姐作伴。”說著拾香來了。嫣娘去了，拾香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又坐在床沿上，引香說：“嫣娘去沒去？”拾香說：“去了。”引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>長嘆了一聲，翻身向里睡著，拾香說：“嫣娘這個人倒不料這樣好性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>格。”引香說：“他好卻好，與我們也是無益。”拾香卻想這夸嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的話說錯了，說：“我不過就人論人，他好也罷，不好也罷，與我們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>甚么相干？”引香又嘆了一口氣說：“像俺兩個。”說到這里，卻縮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>住了口不說了。一時阿粲、宜人都來了。過了幾天，引香原沒大病，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也就好了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    不覺到了十月下旬，一日忽然朔風凜凜刮了一天，到晚上飄起雪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了。嫣娘想去邀引香、拾香、宜人、阿粲明日賞雪，就自己獨步趁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著雪光悄悄的走到聊寄齋窗外，聽著里邊引香說：“我起一句‘幾回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卻寒寒又生’。”宜人說：“我有第二句。”拾香說：“我也有了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”阿粲說：“我也有了。”引香說：“都莫說，寫在紙上，聯完了我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>讀。”嫣娘在窗外聽著，里邊忽然這個高吟，忽然那個低詠，又聽著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一時磨墨，又一時呵墨，又忽聽著一人向桌上一拍說：“我這一句可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>謂大妙，”高聲念道：“侍兒偷看儂風流。”眾人都是喝彩說：“妙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>！妙！”嫣娘聽那高聲念的，卻是引香。一時詩成了，引香說：“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>乏了，宜姐姐念罷。念著我們推敲，有不妙的再刪改刪改。”嫣娘聽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人念道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “幾回卻寒寒又生，侍兒報說已三更。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    床頭剩有浮梁在，且開紅爐再挑燈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    燈火爐火相映紅，無人惱儂誰惱儂？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    依亦無心亦無說，侍兒暖酒味已濃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    獨酌獨坐仍獨飯，欲將酒興溫寒枕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一枕蝴蝶未飛來，教儂怎臥鴛鴦錦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    移時忽覺潮生頰，粉黛頓將秋波壓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    幾點桃花香欲濃，此情無可與歡洽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    豈是有情即不醉，醉后欲睡又懶睡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    侍兒背我已朦朧，謂我何故偏不寐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    更教淺淺酌一杯，誰催玉漏又相催？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    我色不知史漏永，回頭對影自低徊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    我憐我影我難描，反恨瘦影亦大嬌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    問影依醉爾可醉，我欲睡時爾亦消。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    是影是夢太模糊，儂俗向影頻頻呼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    頻頻呼去影不語，儂且耐寒自唏噓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    侍兒促睡不敢言，不言欲言言又難。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    儂卻亦有難言處，謂我侍兒夜未闌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    侍兒勸我卸殘妝，銀杯收畢又商量。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一鉤殘月帘痕破，不管窗前已上霜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    褪去金釵玉搔頭，侍兒偷看儂風流。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    儂今已醉睡不得，侍兒為我閉小樓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    儂已欲睡爾且去，侍兒欲去又回顧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    重來復將獸炭添，為此夜深寒卻不？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    夢里可有消寒術，有術即從夢小住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    睡睡不知夢可成，莫使儂被一夢誤。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    宜人念完了，嫣娘拍著手高聲說：“妙詩，妙詩！”宜人說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不好，有鬼。”拾香說：“這不是鬼，必是詩魔。”說著嫣娘進來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又從新看了一會說：“我方才想請諸位詩翁明日聯句，哪知已經聯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，我明日也不請了。”拾香說：“正為明日要聯句，所以才先作的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”嫣娘說：“這是怎么說的，你講，我聽聽。”拾香說：“你是下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>過場的，不知道凡童生、秀才、舉人去應試，就先備個夾帶嗎？”說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著大家笑起來了。又說了一會說，嫣娘去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    不覺臘盡春初，到了上元佳節，嫣娘就想制燈屏，將園里設詩社</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>燈謎。不知如何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十回  謎罵  春愁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說到了上元佳節，嫣娘這幾日就忙著叫人制了燈屏，又叫人去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>買了各樣花燈，都買來了。嫣娘叫人各處花庭亭閣俱以佳起來，又挂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些在樹枝上，又擺些在各處假山上并各處花塢地下。到了這上元之夕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，嫣娘請了引香眾人一齊俱來看燈，引香眾人都來了。嫣娘同著去看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，看亭子上是百合花燈，又擺著三仙燈、百壽燈、三龍戲珠、三鳳朝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>陽各燈，樹上又挂著各樣飛鳥燈，假山上又擺著蓮花燈，地下又擺著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>幾架鰲山燈。又到了明月清風廬，見正中圍著燈屏，里面挂的擺的各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>樣花燈不一。引香看屏上貼著燈謎，就叫拾香、宜人、阿粲俱來猜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>拾香說：“這貼個白紙條，沒有字，打《西廂》二句，這是個甚么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>若是一句，必是‘盡在不言中’了。”引香想了一想說：“我猜著了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，拿彩來罷！”嫣娘讓姐姐說說，“若不是的，如何給彩哩？”引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“這是‘你不言，我已省’。”拾香說：“這個謎連出的猜的都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有了。”嫣娘送了一串金珠夾苓香的香串。阿粲又看著一個是：“教</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>書代行醫，打《詩經》一句。”阿粲說：“我猜著了，是‘大夫君子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>’。”嫣娘送了吳綾一正。宜人又看了一個是畫了一個似龜非龜的東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>西，駝著一個碑，那駝碑的前爪拿著一面大鑼，打《詩經》一句，送</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>紅緞一疋，銅雀瓦硯一方。宜人想了一想，不解，又叫拾香、阿粲、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>引香俱來猜，都不解。宜人向嫣娘說：“我們實在不知道這個，你向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我們說罷。”拾香說：“莫問他，我定要這一正緞子，一方硯瓦。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又想了一時，笑道：“這個謎真真有些意思。”引香說：“我也不解</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，你知道嗎？”拾香說：“是‘其樂只且’。”引香說：“怎么像？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”拾香說：“上二字‘其樂’原是借‘鑼’字之意，下二字‘只且’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，你想這‘且’字像個甚么？”引香說：“真真像個碑。”宜人說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“這我們如何解得？要能解，還要去問那會敲大鑼的。”說著大家都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑起來了。嫣娘說：“莫猜罷，我們來敲鑼鼓罷。”拾香說：“我是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要彩的。”嫣娘說：“已備齊了，等我過一時著人送去。”引香說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“宜姐、粲姐、拾香他三個都不會敲。”嫣娘說：“娟姐、嫿姐、娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐他們都會。”引香說：“你方才出這個謎，叫誰敲大鑼誰肯敲喔？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“這有何妨，等我五娘來敲。”就鼓鼓通通敲了一個“富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>貴不斷頭”，敲完了，又吃了酒，才各自去了。一連頑了幾天，燈節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>畢了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    不覺到了清明時候，鄭氏著丫頭來叫嫣娘。嫣娘見了鄭氏，鄭氏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我這幾天心里不甚舒服，你明日去給你父掃墓罷。”嫣娘就向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭氏說：“園中奚家姐妹并那些丫頭們天天在園里也是悶悶的，何不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫他們同去？一則干姐妹也當去給父親磕頭，丫頭們也當去的。”鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏說：“好。”嫣娘就去叫家人備了幾乘大轎、小轎，又到園里向他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們說了。第二天各各都收拾齊了。嫣娘看引香、拾香、宜人他們各穿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>單（示夾），俱是湖綢、貢緞、蘇綾、春羅等衣，一齊出了園，到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大庭，上了轎，往塋地去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了塋地，下了轎，家人擺上供養，一齊都行了禮。嫣娘同著眾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人各處看看，見那柳條垂金，桃花如笑，碧草鋪錦，李林堆玉，引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“弟弟，你看這些春景如何？”嫣娘說：“最妙，最妙！”引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“可恨，可恨！”嫣娘正色問說：“姐姐此言胡為乎來？”引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你想，這春光斷不能為人長留，到了夏天，雖然綠樹濃蔭，青</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>山翠疊，似乎茂盛之氣過于春天，而一番嬌艷之色，鮮妍之態，情致</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>纏綿，楚楚動人，則不及春遠矣。此故何也？猶人之愛博而情馳耳！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>到了秋天，那寥寥落落，到了冬天那枯枯槁槁，這春也不知哪里去了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，徒叫人愛春的思春，豈不是這春天故意惹人牽連，到不如不見之為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>愈也。”嫣娘說：“這也是沒法。”引香嘆口氣就轉過臉來向阿粲說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我們回去罷。”宜人、拾香說：“娉姐、娟姐怎么不見？”一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見娉、娟手里拿著許多野花來了，嫿姐、關關、窈窈也掐了些桃花、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>杏花拿著。嫣娘說：“你們看窈姐折了一枝杏花扛在肩上，映著他這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個瘦瘦的臉，紅紅的腮，又搭上映著碧香色的裌衫，白綾畫墨的百蝶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>裙子，遠遠望著，只怕哪會畫美人的也畫不上來這幅春艷圖。”說著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一齊上轎去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了家，都到上房見了鄭氏，又都到園里各自去了。到了晚〔上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>〕，阿粲手提著一個玻璃燈毬，到了明月清風廬，問：“相公可睡？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”娉婷說：“方才睡下。”嫣娘聽著，連忙說：“快請粲姐進來。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>阿粲進來了，嫣娘就要起來，阿粲急急走上床去，將嫣娘按住說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>可莫起來，冒了風不是頑的。”嫣娘就睡下說：“有罪，有罪！”就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>問說：“粲姐這時候來作甚么？”阿粲說：“相小姐、拾小姐請你明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日去做會。”嫣娘說：“做甚么會？”阿粲說：“兩個小姐同我跟宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐商議明日送春，又請這邊各位姐姐明日或是著彩綢，或是用柳條花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>朵做成各樣人馬，明日帶去。”說著又挨著嫣娘的耳朵說：“我在上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭聽說替你訂解元夫人了。”嫣娘笑著說：“沒有的事，我才出服，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你莫來戲弄我了。”阿粲說：“當真，還聽說是個姓許的，他父親在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>外頭做知府才回來，又聽說他家怎么跑了個小廝，說隨前是個姓胡的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說進來的，他家老爺回來將姓胡的打了一頓。嫣娘聽了這句話，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“噯呀，是我害了你了。”阿粲說：“這與相公甚么相干？”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“不是你才說給我說親鬧的嗎？”阿粲說：“不是因為這個，因為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小廝跑了。”嫣娘說：“不管他，你且去罷，我要睡了。”阿粲站起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來就要走，嫣娘說：“娟姐、嫿姐來，你兩個送粲姐過去，這夜深了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>看他害怕，你兩個回來有伴可以不怕的。”娟、嫿同阿粲去了，一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>〔便回〕來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二日，嫣娘就催著娟、嫿他五個各制了彩綢、柳花人馬一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>齊去了。到了〔聊寄〕齋，引香四個人接進去，引香說：“我今且請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你來替這春光送送行，這對面亭子上就當個餞別的長亭。”坐了一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，一齊上了亭。引香叫拾香去叫丫頭將果盒子捧來，放在亭內小圓桌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上，上設了一個座位。一時娟、嫿、娉婷、關、窈都來了，引香接著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他幾個，一齊將各制的小綢人、小綢馬，柳條編的小馬、小人，上頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又插些花，都放在亭外地下，宜人、阿粲也去將各制的小人小馬都拿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來放在亭外地下，嫣娘說：“這儀仗不全。”引香說：“是了，這是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>群花的，沒有花神的。”又叫丫頭拿些彩綢、柳條來，引香同著他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著彩綢粘了小八人轎、八個小轎夫，又粘了一輛轎車，又粘了許多小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人，趕車的、打執事的，又粘了兩小旗、小傘、小幡、小鑼給他拿著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又將柳條編了些小馬給人騎著，駕著車，都放在亭子外邊，一齊都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>到亭子內坐下，嫣娘向上邊座位上說：“春哥哥、春姐姐，你們回去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，明年早些來我家，引姐姐、拾妹妹并娟姐、嫿姐、娉姐、宜姐、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>粲姐、窈姐、關姐都是時時刻刻想你的，就是我這不才，也不敢忘了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你的。”又斟了一杯酒說：“你也不要想我們，莫想瘦了，你明年來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，我們都不認得了。”引的眾人都笑起來。引香說：“你倒有些婆子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氣。”嫣娘說：“你們都不出聲，這春哥哥、春姐姐如何知道呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說著又下來向上邊作了一個揖，說：“恕我不行全禮了。”引香說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“莫鬧笑話了，坐著吃酒罷。”吃了幾杯，嫣娘忽然掉下淚來，拾香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你這個人真是瘋魔了，常解元好好的，哭甚么？”引香說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我知道。”嫣娘只當他真知道昨日胡小廝的話，就說：“我是為你們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>送春惹的。”拾香說：“不是的，只怕是哥哥想吃干母的酒罷。”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘說：“也不是的。我是想春光去了，古人說‘天若有情天亦老’，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>可是天為無情方才不老。這春也是無情，為何也有老的時候？人家詞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上說：‘春光老’，你我們這些人不是草木，焉能無情？這‘老’之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一字是難免了。可憐我們今日送春，不知可被這春笑煞我們說，‘我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春光去了，還有來的時候，你們到青春，一去卻再想來就不能了’。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說到這里，大家都轉喜為悲。正在感慨，忽然來了一個丫頭說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“奶奶請相公。”嫣娘就去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    見了鄭氏，鄭氏說：“前日有個人來替你說親，是姓許，在三山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>街上住，現在做知府。這家沒有兒子，只有這一個女兒。這家原是在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>杭州住，新搬來的，是我們家的表親，因為住的遠，所以不常往來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我想甚好，不知你可願意？”嫣娘說：“這些事自是母親作主，母親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>看著怎么好就怎么好，何用問兒子呢？”說畢，坐了一時就回園來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了園，看他五個都回來了。娉婷問說：“奶奶請你作甚么？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘笑了一笑說：“沒甚事。”到了晚上，嫣娘只推著說天熱了，屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里人多更熱，叫娟、嫿、關、窈都到那邊櫥子里去睡，他四個都搬去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。嫣娘到屋睡下，娉婷將燈挪遠了些，也睡下。嫣娘說：“我如今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也不想活了。”娉婷說：“這從哪里說起？”嫣娘說：“你們有事都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>瞞著我，我成個孤鴻落沙灘了，活著有甚么趣？”娉婷說：“我沒瞞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>過你。”嫣娘說：“你既然是真心，不瞞我，就發個誓。”娉婷說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“我有事要瞞你，就立刻死了。”嫣娘說：“這不瞞我，姐姐果然是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>真心了。”就問說：“你家富春小姐到底如何？”娉婷不答應，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“我這園里的神最靈，你不說，一時就要犯誓了。”娉婷說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我前日不是向你說了嗎？”嫣娘說：“那是說個大概。”娉婷說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這一一細說，我也說不上來。我又不會寫真，畫個小照給你看看。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又說：“我那小姐的丹青卻是第一，詩才也是第一，只怕引小姐未必</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是他的對手。”嫣娘說：“我南京解元常敏，乳名嫣娘，排行五娘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”說著又披衣坐起，合掌念道：“阿彌陀佛，是那有這樣福分！”娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷說：“怎么說？我不懂。”嫣娘大笑了幾聲說：“我沒發誓，我可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要瞞你了。”娉婷又問他，他就始而裝睡，忽而真睡了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二天，丫頭來請嫣娘，嫣娘就到上房去了。見了鄭氏，鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏向他商議納聘的話，又叫李立請陰陽排日子，今年秋天迎娶。又過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了幾天，納了聘。不覺到了秋天，天天忙著，各事備齊，又將明月清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>風廬收拾做了新房，將娟、嫿五個挪在右邊所所去住。不知這過門如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何熱鬧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十一回  閨謔  齋別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說喜事諸物俱以齊備，到了吉期，那親迎拜堂，一番熱熱鬧鬧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，是不須多贅。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說富春過了三朝，就著跟來的雁奴去喚了娉婷來。這時恰好嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘不在房里，娉婷來了，富春問說：“我一來的時候，便看見你了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>后來又看見你來這，嫣娘幾次〔在〕，我總不得空問你。”娉婷聽富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春說到這里，就眼圈一紅說：“我在老太太跟前，老太太實在疼我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>總是我自己無福，肯惹老太太生氣，所以老太太打發了我，我也未得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去給小姐磕頭，與雁奴妹子辭行。”說著就掉下幾點淚來。富春說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“你怎么湊巧就到這里來了，我與你雖非他鄉，卻也算遇故知了。但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是我有一件不明白的事，你來的久自然是知道的，你不要瞞我。我問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你自家大爺往我家去親迎拜三，如何家里老太太、老爺并下邊的家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>俱說像那年來投向的王貴一樣？”娉婷聽了，卻不好答應、又不敢不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>答應，只說：“你像王貴或者是王貴也未可知，但大爺明明姓常名敏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又明明是解元，如何肯當做小廝的王貴？說這或者是人之面貌相同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”富春說：“你怎么又剛剛賣到這像王貴的常敏家呢？”娉婷卻答</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>應不上來，只說：“這卻連我也不知道。”富春說：“這卻連我也未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必不知道。”娉婷就連忙跪下說：“娉婷若有不遵小姐素日所訓‘貞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>節’二字，願世世不得人身。”富春笑了一笑，叫雁奴拉起來，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“可以我為醋海中人乎？我若如此，子當聞酸風而堂余光焉！你從實</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>對我說罷。”娉婷含羞帶笑，把前事一一告于富春。富春聽完了，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑了一笑說：“我以先正想我跟你與雁奴不能一生常聚，此正如吾之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>願。”雁奴說：“姐姐，你們花園里的事，我怎么不知道？”富春笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，“噯喲”了一聲說：“你要早知道了，我的那個水晶瓶也要碎了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”娉婷聽著，把臉紅了又紅。忽聽院里腳步響，雁奴跑出來一看，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“大爺回來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘進了屋，看著富春在那里笑，娉婷在旁站著紅著臉。娉婷見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘來了，瞅了他一眼就出去了。嫣娘就里間坐下，問富春說：“小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐笑甚么？”富春說：“笑你真真是個有才的。”嫣娘說：“我這庸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>夫俗子知道甚么？像小姐，是超織錦之奇，畫過描鳳之巧，又這樣貌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>比王嬙而王嬙猶輸一著，色比西子而西子亦讓三分，可謂佳人而才子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>者也。”富春說：“大爺之言我固不敢當，然即如是，亦不及大爺這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>種才情，這樣人品，又這樣芳名，嫣娘可謂才子而佳人者也！不特可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>謂這樣才子而佳人，又可謂那樣才子而家人者也！”富春說著，卻笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個沒了。嫣娘說：“這有甚么可笑的？”富春說：“我要不笑，我可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就要待小人不惡而嚴了，說王貴你好大膽，我們小姐在這里坐著，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也敢坐著，來跪下！”嫣娘說：“跪下我情願。”說著就跪下說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>解元常敏稟見。”富春笑的氣喘不過來，說：“王小廝，你怎么敢私</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>入花園，實實供來！”嫣娘說：“小的不敢！”富春又笑著說：“王</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小廝，你怎么敢拐騙人口？”嫣娘說：“小的實在不敢，請解元夫人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、王小廝仆婦發落！”富春笑著說：“你怎么把我也遭塌起來了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說著笑彎了腰說：“你嘔死我了，罷了，罷了，姑寬可也。”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“謝解元夫人釋放，小廝仆婦大赦。”說著也笑的氣喘不過來。富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春說：“你起來，我與你說正經話。”嫣娘起來作個揖說：“小姐有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何下諭？”富春說：“坐下罷，真鬧了。”又叫雁奴說：“你笑還未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑夠？去給我倒茶。”雁奴笑著去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘說：“甚么正經話？”富春說：“你可知道奚家姐妹要搬回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去了！”嫣娘把臉色一變說：“可是真話？”富春說：“是奚伯母前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日來說奚老伯來家了，把他姊妹接回去住幾天，說老伯還要出門。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說：“奚老伯再出門，自然是引姐姐、拾妹妹還要進來的。”富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春說：“只怕未必。”嫣娘把眉一皺說：“這是惹個，莫是我得罪他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們了？”富春說：“依我看來，也不是你得罪，就是老伯來家來接他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們的話也是個飾詞。”嫣娘說：“怎么樣聽？”富春說：“這不難懂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，因為你如今成了親，是成人了。你們雖是姐妹，畢竟是個異姓，住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在一塊不方便的意思。”嫣娘說：“天下人要個個如此多心，像這日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子我也過不成了。”富春說：“你是個解元，自然是文理通的了，難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>道人情說不通嗎？且無論奚家姐妹之事，你一時高興跑在我們園里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>把娉婷千方百計買了來。雖然是你憐香惜玉之情，然非我知娉婷之真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又知你之切，亦不免有些疑心了。況男女避嫌，禮之宜然，奚家姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>妹如何不當去的呢？”嫣娘就作了一揖說：“你真真是一口涼水，叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我吞下，頓使肺腑生風。但是我們姐妹一場，我想去給他話別一番，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不知小姐可許否？”富春把眉一瞅，臉一變，正色說：“你把我當作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何人？床頭夜叉非我富春也！且人孰無情，用之于正，惟恐其薄。奚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>家姐妹我跟他也是甚親熟的，我也想去看看才好。何況你們雖不是從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小姐妹，也是在一塊過了幾年的，一旦舍去，豈不大家都難分手的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你就先去，我到晚再去。”嫣娘就去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了聊寄齋，引香、拾香并宜人、阿粲接著。進屋坐下。嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“姐姐、妹妹就在這里住著，雖不十分如意，也可將就，為何又要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>回去？”引香不答應，拾香說：“‘將就’二字，豈是長策？我們在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你家住著，畢竟算個甚么？”嫣娘說：“妹妹之言，我也不敢分辯，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>只是聚首將近三年，姐姐、妹妹一旦舍我而去，如我濁物，姐姐、妹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>妹自然覺一日不見此濁物便清亮許多了。只是我與姐妹相處之久，姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐、妹妹不替我想想，我如何過得？”引香說：“各人顧各人，我不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>能替你，你也不能替我。”說到這里，他三個就無言對泣，宜人、阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>粲想勸也沒話可說，只是陪著下淚。過了一時，引香說：“我們這是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何必？豈不是把好光陰虛度了？”一句未說完，只看宜人、阿粲抱頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大哭，倒是引香、拾香來勸住了他兩個。嫣娘說：“你兩個這大哭又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>從哪路而來？”宜人說：“人心不同，相感則一。今日之宜人、阿粲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，固無殊于引小姐、拾小姐也！”嫣娘說：“噯！是我薄命，不能同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>引姐姐、拾妹妹常在一處看花燈、猜啞謎、踏青送春，倒連累了引姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐、拾妹妹今日這一回頭惱并宜姐粲姐這一回傷心。”正在說著，丫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭來說：“奶奶請兩位小姐。”嫣娘問說：“做甚么？”丫頭說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是請小姐們到上房用飯，今晚上奶奶因二位小姐回去特特備的，已經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著人去請少奶奶去了。”說著引香、拾香起來向嫣娘說：“我也不到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>貴處去辭行了。”又與宜人、阿粲辭了一辭。嫣娘同宜人、阿粲送到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>處處的洞門才回來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘又到聊寄齋坐下，問宜人說：“你們兩個在這里住著，豈不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>太寂寞了，我叫嫿姐來與你們作伴。”阿粲說：“人若不寂寞，就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一個人住著也不寂寞；若是寂寞，就是一百個人住著也是寂寞。這寂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>寞卻不在人之多少。”宜人說：“你回去叫嫿姐來也好，只是我這邊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>添一個，他那邊不又少一個，不覺著他們一處住慣的，忽然分離了嗎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”嫣娘說：“總是在一處，相離也不遠。”宜人說：“依我看著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卻是‘劉郎已恨蓬山遠，更隔蓬山一萬重’。”嫣娘聽著，嘆了一口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氣，帶淚而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了明月清風廬，見雁奴及娉婷在那里坐著。見了嫣娘來都站起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來，雁奴說：“姑奶奶說了，叫娉姐搬到這里住罷，同我都在那邊櫥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子里。”嫣娘點點頭，也不坐下，又出去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一直到了所所那邊。正在走著，忽聽一個人說：“我們到底怎么</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了？”嫣娘聽著就停住了腳，又聽一個人說：“這只好隨他了。”說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著又嘆了口氣。嫣娘聽著，在那一塊太湖石前邊，這石頭后邊，都是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>小紫竹子。嫣娘就分開竹子慢慢進去，走到跟前方才蹲下，等了一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卻不聽動靜，又起來轉過前面，卻不見一人，心里想著：“方才明明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一個像娟姐，一個像關姐，說話如何不見了？真真是《西廂》上說的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>‘難道是昨夜夢中來’。只是夜里好作夢。這無將黃昏尚未到夜里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我如何就作起夢來了？”想著就往那正房走，走未幾步，忽聽一個人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>背后叫他，說：“天黑了，你怎么一個人來這大地方來？”嫣娘轉過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>臉來一看，卻是嫿姐。嫣娘說：“我是來作價的。”嫿姐說：“請誰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”嫣娘說：“恭請足下。”嫿姐說：“這時候又不牽親，又不上頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，請我作甚么？”嫣娘說：“前日有勞，今日踵門拜謝，還請與宜、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>粲二位作伴。”嫿姐說：“這個事正該用著我，我們好惺惺惜惺惺了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”嫣娘說：“姐姐莫忙。”嫿姐正色問說：“怎么莫忙？我又有甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么忙的？”嫣娘笑了一笑說：“有罪，有罪，失言求恕！”又問他三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個哪里去了，嫿姐說：“方才都在這里，我看娟姐、關姐在那太湖石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>下坐了一會不知哪里去了，窈姐是在屋里繡手帕子，娉姐今日不來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”嫣娘說：“我知道，天黑了，我也不到屋〔里〕了，你見了他三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個替我說我來看他們罷，你也就去罷。”說著嫣娘回來，到了明月清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>風廬，坐下問雁奴說：“我去了，你姑奶奶可有話說我甚么？”雁奴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑了一笑說：“大爺的話說錯了，‘為人不作虧心事，何怕半夜鬼敲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>門’，我姑奶奶有甚么子說你的，你想想你有甚么可說的，姑奶奶就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說你甚么。”嫣娘笑著說：“你可算一位副將軍，真是‘殺人如草不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聞聲’。”雁奴說：“我卻沒殺人，倒拐了一個人。”娉婷聽著，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起來將雁奴捺在椅子上膈肢他，雁奴笑的只落喘氣，說：“好姐姐，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我說話不與你相干。”娉婷說：“正為不與我相干，我才膈肢你，這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>才是‘公道自在人心’。”娉婷說著，又去膈肢，雁奴說：“好姐姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，我再不敢了。”嫣娘說：“罷了，饒了他罷。”娉婷松了手，雁奴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起來，嫣娘說：“你看你的金釵也退了，頭發也散了。”說著就起來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>拿個小梳子替他攏一攏，說：“看你姑奶奶來看著，又要嚷你們淘氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”將才收拾完，只見兩個丫頭提著燈籠，引著富春來了。進了里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>間，叫兩個丫頭回去。坐了一時，嫣娘又問他引香、拾香去的話。說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了一會，富春說：“恭喜”。嫣娘說：“甚么喜？”富春說：“到明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日你自然知道。”嫣娘問他，他總不說。不知是甚么喜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十二回  寫春  來鳳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘問富春怎樣恭喜，富春總不說，嫣娘也只得罷了。到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>第二日，一早丫頭來說：“老太太叫大爺。”嫣娘去了。到了上房，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭氏說：“你好造化！”嫣娘說：“兒子沒甚造化。”鄭氏說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>媳婦昨日沒向你說嗎？”嫣娘說：“沒有。”鄭氏笑了一笑說：“這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>孩子也算會做事的，這是要叫我開口的意思。”嫣娘說：“到底是甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么事？”鄭氏說：“我昨日叫他來送你干姐妹，你干姐妹去了，他向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我說園中自宜人以下有阿粲、娉婷、娟、嫿、關、窈這些人，又添上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我帶來的雁奴，個個俱是才貌雙全，我想一并求老太太恩典賞給他收</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在房里罷。一則他們都是相處甚久，如今若是打發了他們，他們必不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>肯去；再則我心里也不忍，就是后來家務也可幫幫我了。他這樣說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我倒喜歡這孩子賢德，不知你可願意？”嫣娘不好應承的，說：“未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>免太多了些。”鄭氏說：“你想去哪幾個？”嫣娘說：“也沒有可去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的。”鄭氏說：“就是這樣好，依你媳婦的話不錯。”嫣娘說：“這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是母親的大恩。”說著就跪下磕了兩個頭。鄭氏說：“你到園里去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我過一時再叫你，去罷！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘到了園里，進了明月清風廬，又進了里間，看富春在妝台前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>坐著，正在曉妝，嫣娘笑著，恭恭敬敬作了兩個揖。富春說：“你瘋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”嫣娘說：“我倒沒瘋，只怕是你瘋了。”富春說：“怎么是我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>瘋了？”嫣娘說：“你說你不瘋，你勸著母親叫我收他們。明日我收</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了他們，我就今日在此，明日在彼，不給你打個照面，那時候，只怕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>解元夫人高居蓮幕，有名無實，悔之晚矣！”富春說：“雁奴過來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去叫娉婷也來。”雁奴不知作甚么，就去叫娉婷來了。富春說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個把我們小廝推出去。”他兩個笑著把嫣娘推出里間，富春又叫將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>門關上。嫣娘在外又是敲門，又是懇求，總不開門。過了一時，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聽屋里唧唧噥噥，一時又微微的笑，就在門縫里偷偷的一看，看著富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春叫娉婷坐下給他開了臉，又叫雁怒坐下，也給他開了臉；又替他兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個梳了個長生不老的頭，又拿些釵釧給他戴上，又拿些新鮮衣裙給他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>穿上。收拾畢了，富春自己開了門，哪知嫣娘正在頭靠著門往里望，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不妨門一開，就一跤扑在門里地下，富春大笑說：“真真是妻不如妾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，方才給我作揖，見了他兩個你就磕起頭來了。”嫣娘扒起來，笑著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>給富春作了一揖說：“有勞有勞，多謝我謝！”正在說著，丫頭來說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“老太太說叫少奶奶各處去給他們開臉，收拾完了，就帶到上房去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”富春答應著，就叫娉婷、雁奴跟著到了處處。進了聊寄齋，嫿姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>三個人接著，富春說：“三個小奶奶，恭喜！”他三個紅著臉也不出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聲，富春就給宜人、阿粲、嫿姐俱開了臉，又叫他們換了新衣，又說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我現在〔成了〕牡丹，百花隊里的花王。你三個也跟我到所所去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”他三個倒不好意思的，也不出聲，只得跟著去了。走到所所的正</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>房，進了屋，關關、窈窈接著，說：“少奶奶跟姐姐們今日往哪里去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”窈妹說：“我也帶你走個人家。”關關說：“往誰家去？”富春</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“往你家去。”又問娟姐哪里去了，關關說：“不知他哪里去了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”富春說：“你去找他來。”關關去了。富春就給窈窈開了臉，換</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了衣裙。一時關關、娟姐來了，他兩個都已明白了，進來見了富春，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>只是臉上紅紅的，富春說：“你兩個新貴人也坐下罷，好給你們開臉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”又把娟、關收拾畢了，富春坐下向上一望說：“這屋里如何無匾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？可以今日之事作個匾額以記其盛，名為‘攜艷館’罷。”又叫他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>都站在一排，富春起來一看，看過說：‘可惜’二字，今日到臨到我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頭上來了！假使我是個男子，真真‘任是無情也動人’。你們跟我到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>上房去罷。”富春走著，宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴、娟、嫿、關、窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>俱跟在后邊，真是過去香生，踏來春嫩，又有那一派環珮叮咚，如仙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子下界一般。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了上房，富春也給鄭氏磕了頭，說：“給老太太道喜。”又叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人他們一字排開給老太太磕了頭，老太太又叫他們，說：“給你們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奶奶磕頭，以后只叫奶奶，不許叫少奶奶了。”富春說：“還未給他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>們爺磕頭，我何敢先收了禮！”鄭氏說：“這便宜他們爺就太多了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>都是你〔賢〕惠能逮下禮，應該叫嫣娘來給你磕個頭才是！”富春笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著說：“老太太這是喜歡極了的話。”鄭氏又各各賞了些釵釧、衣裙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>料。鄭氏向富春說：“你領他們去罷。”富春領著要走，鄭氏說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你們還等一時。”又叫丫頭去叫了嫣娘來。嫣娘來了，見了鄭氏，給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭氏磕頭道喜，鄭氏又叫宜人他們給嫣娘磕頭，鄭氏說：“你如今心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里也足了，以后凡事總要聽你媳婦的話，這孩子比你明白多咧！”嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘答應著，又望著富春笑了一笑。鄭氏說：“都去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一齊到了園里，宜人八個都跟著嫣娘、富春進了明月清風廬。嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘、富春坐下，宜人八個站在旁邊，富春說：“你們仍是照舊住著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>明日是端午佳節，我方才看亭子外邊池子里的荷花也開了幾朵，明日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我同你們到亭子上賞荷，就算給你們吃團圓酒，都去歇歇罷。”宜人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>六個去了。富春又向嫣娘說：“你同這兩個新娘子也去坐個床罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘笑著說：“慌甚么。”富春說：“我可不得陪了。”說著進了里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>間，叫雁奴來說：“你今日暫陪我一陪，你把這長幾擺開，鋪上紅氈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，拿塊素絹來，再把各樣顏色碟子拿來。”雁奴一一都收拾好了，富</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春就拈起筆來畫個工筆小圖，先把鏡台擺在面前，照著鏡子畫了自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的小照，又畫了宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴、娟、嫿、關、窈各各的小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>像，或是觀花，或是看柳，或是整理云鬟，或是小立石畔，即名為《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>攜艷圖》，足足畫了半天，又畫了大半夜。到四更畫畢，收拾睡下，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>問雁奴說：“大爺哪里去了？”雁奴將手向那邊一指，又笑了一笑，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>富春說：“你就在這凳子上睡罷，莫驚散了鴛鴦夢不成，不然又要并</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>蒂花開連理枝了。”雁奴笑著也睡下了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到第二日一早，宜人六個俱來給富春請安，富春叫他們俱在明月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>清風廬吃了飯，一齊到亭子上去。富春憑欄而看，見那荷花靜香襲人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，幽艷悅目，說：“這時候大爺一個人在屋里，不知急的怎么樣？我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來也沒請他，他自然是不好來的。”向宜人說：“你去請大爺去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人去了，見了嫣娘，嫣娘問說：“你來作甚么？”宜人說：“奶奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>請你。”嫣娘說：“你坐下，我跟你說話。”宜人說：“爺跟前我如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何敢坐。”嫣娘說：“你怎么如今到生分了？”說著笑了一笑，拉宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人坐在一塊說：“如今我才知道你真不嫌我了。”又笑了一笑說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我比李立何如？”宜人說：“你也不可太高興了，明日我們同奶奶將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你捆起來審審你，問這拐騙人口一案。”宜人又說：“快罷，莫去遲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。”說著都站起來，宜人將嫣娘衣服一掀說：“我看看膝蓋跪腫了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>沒有？”一會又說：“小的不敢了。”說著笑著一齊出了屋。到了亭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子，富春接著進了亭子，叫丫頭將四面格子俱以開了，望著池子的荷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>花。又叫丫頭將席擺上，用一大圓桌，富春說：“這是取團圓之意。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”又叫宜人八個都坐下，又叫丫頭去把《攜艷圖》拿來遞給嫣娘，叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他一一對著人去看看，看可像不像。嫣娘看了一會，又看了他們九個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，真真一般。嫣娘贊了一會，富春又叫丫頭去拿了筆硯來，就在圖后</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>各題一贊，作五古一絕，題畢遞給嫣娘看。嫣娘說：“夫人有贊，爾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>等各宜敬聽可也。”富春說：“你真有些孩子氣，這幾句話如何又裝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>出戲上道白的樣子來。”嫣娘說：“莫說了，聽我念罷。”題宜人的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    我向眾香國，細問爾前身。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    風流那可說，只覺爾宜人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    阿粲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    今夕何夕兮，我見此粲者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    這樣巧樣妝，阿儂為誰也？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娉婷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娉婷復娉婷，宜向東風立。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    不讓柳生春，三眠又三起。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    雁奴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    莫向秋風飛，秋風寒栗栗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    這般翠羽衣，如何禁得起？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娟姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    可是巫山女，可是月宮仙？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    娟姐此一字，肯不付嬋娟？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫿姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    妖嬈亦姽嫿，有情何多情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    只愁風流樣，畫工畫不成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    關關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    雎鳩乎關關，爾正可為匹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    詩先得我心，已從許第一。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    窈窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    十五小女郎，窈窈真窈窈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    我聞笑語聲，一點櫻桃小。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘讀畢，拍手大笑說：“妙，妙，妙，妙！”宜人八個一齊說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我們這婢子如何當得起，若奶奶則是集群美于一身，凡我輩之所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有奶奶則兼之矣。”說著又吃了一會酒，富春說：“我聽〔說〕宜姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、粲姐俱善彈琴，何不對我牛一彈？”宜人、阿粲連忙站起來說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不過是略解宮商，奶奶若不厭煩，可以彈彈。”就叫丫頭去抱了兩張</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>琴來，宜人、阿粲各理琴弦，彈了一會，富春說：“我最喜歡的是吹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>簫，若是以簫和琴，則更是洋洋盈耳。”嫣娘說：“這不難。我前日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>在一親戚家吃酒，有個女（女當）子叫個么鳳，善于吹簫，他這管簫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也是個富翁送他的，是羊脂玉雕成的。”富春說：“這女（女當）子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>顏色如何？”嫣娘笑了一笑說：“也可在這里坐得。”富春說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何不著人去叫來。”嫣娘就起來，到前面找著李立說了一會。這女（</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>女當）子本是嫣娘素所物色的，今日恰恰得了這個機會，就叫李立去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說著買他，李立去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘來到亭子上，向富春說：“一時么鳳即來。”富春同宜人幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個一齊吃酒畢了，俱到明月清風廬。天將申酉，一個丫頭引著一個女</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>（女當）子來了。到了屋，給嫣娘、富春磕了頭，又向宜人他們問候</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。富春說：“你的簫吹的是好的，請你來，領領妙音。”么鳳說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“本不善吹，奶奶要聽，且吹一支聽聽。”就拿出來一管白玉簫吹著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。嫣娘就趁空出去了。富春聽他吹簫，看他那兩只手與玉簫互相輝映</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，那一點朱唇挨著玉簫，如朱砂班兒相似，不時的夸獎。一時嫣娘來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，富春說：“可以送他去罷。”嫣娘說：“他不去了。”富春說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“你留著明日還吹不成？”嫣娘說：“因為你喜歡，我已經著二百銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子買下來了。”富春只當是頑話，說：“好，明日我也求老太太給你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>收下。”嫣娘就起來作個揖說：“好好，你始終成全成全我罷。”說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著就逼著富春就去，富春說：“果真你買了嗎？你也可謂貪心不足。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”富春沒了法，只得到了上房替他周旋著，將么鳳領去見了鄭氏，磕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了頭，給他收下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    回到明月清風廬，富春向嫣娘說：“你如何謝媒？”嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>要甚么就有甚么。”富春說：“今日頗熱，我在院里乘涼，你只管自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>便。我叫么鳳吹簫，我聽《暫誤錦帳春風》，就算謝媒罷，不知你願</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>意不願意？”嫣娘笑著說：“情願，情願。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了晚上，富春叫么鳳吹簫。吹到三更，一時下起雨來，夜深頗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>覺寒了。富春叫丫頭將么鳳送到所所去住，他又坐了一時，也睡了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>睡到五更，忽覺身上發熱。不知是病不是病。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十三回  香消  月圓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說富春身上發熱，到了第二日，果然就大病起來了。嫣娘忙著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>請了郎中來診了脈，卻是受了風寒。用了藥，服了數劑總未見效。嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘又請了一個郎中來看了脈說：“病轉少陰，頗覺沉重。”又服了幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>劑亦未見效。鄭氏一日數次來看，嫣娘同宜人幾個時時守著，更是不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>必說了。一連病了半月，起先總是昏昏沉沉睡著不應，許老太太、許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>老爺、許太太都是天天來看，也無非忙著請醫問卜，總是不見少減。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了二十日以外，一日，嫣娘同宜人幾個旁邊守著、望著他，忽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見富春睜開眼向嫣娘點點頭，嫣娘在床沿坐著，又向前一挪，靠近問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他說：“心里如何？”又著手去摸摸他的頭，富春一手拉住嫣娘的手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，微微嘆了兩聲，悲悲切切，有欲泣之狀，卻又無淚；又使著力氣慢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>慢地說：“是我誤了你了。”嫣娘聽著，慟不可言，柔腸寸斷，又不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>敢遽然放聲，恐病人添了傷心。富春又說：“我去后，宜人是不錯的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，你當另加青盼，諸人亦非樗櫟，你惜花的工夫亦不可太省了。”說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著覺氣不接，喘了一時，宜人幾個說：“奶奶靜養靜養罷，莫煩心了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”富春又把眼一睜，喘著氣說：“再想在荷花亭上看花，同你們吃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>酒。”說著，望著宜人、阿粲說：“聽你兩個彈琴。”又望著么鳳說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“聽你吹簫，再不能了。”說著又喘了幾口氣。嫣娘說：“莫說罷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，太勞神了，歇歇罷。”富春喘著說：“我死。”說到這里，那氣又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>接不上來，嫣娘、宜人幾個聽著真是心如芒刺，只是噙著淚不敢下落</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，這無聲之泣更甚于有聲了。富春又喘了一時，說：“我死后，你家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雖是有余，但我乃幼喪，不可太費，有違于理，外人也是笑話你的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”說著又喘了幾口氣，又向著宜人說：“你們幾個好好服事爺罷。爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>之有不精明處，你們要放明白些，總要到喜歡處不可忘了煩惱，‘發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>乎情，止乎禮’，這就是我們閨閣中的淑女了。”說著氣又不接，捱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了一時，又向嫣娘說：“婆婆面前我未得盡一日之孝，我更是罪人了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”說著氣喘的就了不得，又使著力氣向嫣娘說：“你莫要想我了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”一句將完，喉中格然一聲，就花落香散了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘抱頭大哭，宜人幾個也是哭的死去活來。丫頭連忙去告于鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏，鄭氏聽著腿都軟了，四個丫頭扶著來到明月清風廬，一路“心肝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的”、“兒的”哭了來，進了里間就大哭一場，又叫丫頭們將嫣娘扶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>過來，說：“他是才絕氣的人，不可太挨近了。”鄭氏就忙著叫丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去叫家人向許老爺那邊通知，又叫丫頭去叫李立辦后事。一時李立著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人將棺木抬進來，這棺木是五百銀子買的，鄭氏、嫣娘看著卻也如意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。一時許老太太、許老爺、許太太俱來了，不免又是大哭起來。一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>入了殮，籍了口，許老太太、許太太又哭了一場去了。鄭氏叫嫣娘留</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著許老爺商議如何開吊，如何誦經，如何設祭，許老爺說：“這些事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你自己酌量，莫說我止有此女，你就過于丰費了。”又說：“我若在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這里看著，卻叫我太傷心了，不如我回去，著我繼子來祭奠他罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說畢又哭了一會就回去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘同宜人幾個天天的哭是不必說的。到了七日，李立領著家人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>先幾日將各處庭房書房以及園內孝棚等物俱以辦齊，因是幼喪，不用</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>白布，俱用白綾、碧色綢緞結彩鋪設。這七日一連三天各處親戚祭奠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，至僧道誦經禮懺一番舉動是不必說了。七日這晚上是大祭，嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“不必作樂，只我領著宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴、娟、嫿、關、窈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、么鳳哭奠哭奠，盡盡心，倒比他們吹吹打打的好些。”到了晚上，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘穿著素服，宜人幾個俱穿著孝服，嫣娘叫他們親自捧帛上菜點酒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，嫣娘到靈前拜了兩拜，跪下拈了三柱香，叫拿筆硯來，就跪在靈前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>以淚研墨，作了一篇祭文，是五言長排，作畢讀道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “期服夫常敏謹具□□不腆致祭于我夫人之靈前，揮淚而告之曰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    奠爾吁嗟爾，知乎與不知？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    辛酸雙眼淚，綿緲寸心思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    驚散鴛鴦鳥，分開蛺蝶枝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    可憐同室日，未至隔年期。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    賢莫違夫子，恩能逮侍兒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    生多承母愛，死尚念親慈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    羞學黃鶯妒，貪看紫燕嬉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一圖攜綺艷，短句品瓊姬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    池畔伊迎我，亭前我問伊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    宜人琴許弄，么鳳管教吹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    解語花為貌，生香玉作肌。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    何須調粉黛，詎屑染胭脂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    并坐常開笑，催妝未畫眉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    琢磨閨閣友，勸勉鏡台師。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    造物偏多忌，人間竟永辭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    神示無可禱，和、緩不能醫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    鬼谷途應險，弓鞋步怎移？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    汝成離女幻，儂作夜郎悲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    昔語芙蓉帳，今傷薛荔帷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    慨無嘆我以，恨未詠螽斯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    雨至怨偏早，春回望稍遲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    想來腰似柳，記得鬢如絲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    誰促香花落，相催細草萎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    堂空人寂寞，弦斷韻鳴咿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    寒暖言惟爾，商量欲向誰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    魄消何有所，骨立已如茲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    縱賴群芳在，難寬片念私。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    木犀然一鼎，玳瑁獻三卮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    情感原無極，神傷不可支。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    千呼仍萬喚，令我幾噫噫！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    尚饗！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘讀畢，伏地放聲大哭，宜人幾個俱放聲大哭，哭了半夜才各</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>止了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    鄭氏以幼喪不宜久停，過了七日就擇了日子葬了。這送葬的一番</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>事自然是各樣俱全，不必說了。嫣娘送葬畢，回到園里又大哭起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人幾個勸了一會方才止住，又進了里間，看床帳依然，人則歸于無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何有矣！嫣娘到妝台跟前，將鏡幅掀開，向鏡中一照，就照鏡子一拍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，哭說：“鏡子呀，自今以后，你這里邊也無有你主人的形像了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>又看著粉妝胭脂等物，又拿過來說：“粉與胭脂，你主人雖不常用你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，如今是大總的謝絕了。”又回頭看著床帳，就跑在床上一歪身睡下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>大哭說：“可憐，可憐！衾也冷了，枕也單了。你兩個有情，也是要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>傷心的了。”又拍著床說：“你如今也太苦了。我往日喜喜歡歡，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也聽些笑語，今日你只聽的是哭聲了。可憐，可憐呀！”宜人幾個上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>前勸說：“奶奶這樣的人一旦仙去，誰不慟慟，但是爺的身子也是要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>緊的。若是哭壞了，就是奶奶心里也不安。你叫他神靈悵帳，這不是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你想他，是你惹他悲傷了。”嫣娘哭著拍著床說：“這不是奶奶坐的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>地方嗎？可憐他不坐了。”又指著地下說：“這不是奶奶站的地方嗎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？可憐他也不站了。”又望著宜人幾個說：“奶奶也不叫你宜姐、粲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐、娟姐、嫿姐、關姐、窈姐、鳳姐了，也不叫娉婷梳頭了，也不叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雁奴添香了，可憐，可憐！”嫣娘說著哭著，哭個不止。丫頭來說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“老太太打發人來，說園中的事情叫宜人照看，可以就搬到這正房來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>住，早晚勸著爺不要多哭了。”嫣娘聽了，答應著，也就暫且飲泣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    過了幾天，嫣娘自是時時傷心，外邊就有幾家來提親的，也有嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘知道的，也有嫣娘不知道的。在嫣娘的意思想以宜人為正，嫣娘也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>微露其意于他母親，鄭氏不肯。鄭氏一日無事，叫人去請李氏來談談</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。李氏來了，鄭氏與李氏談了半天，李氏問鄭氏說：“大侄自然是要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>續娶的，不知可有成議沒有？”鄭氏把眼圈兒一紅，掉下淚來，說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“親是提了幾家，我總怕不能抵上我那媳婦。”說著那淚就扑簌簌的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>滾下來了。李氏勸了一時，又坐了一時去了。鄭氏想著引香甚好，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是跟嫣娘在一塊住過的，嫣娘自然是願意的，就叫丫頭去請了李立來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。李立來了，鄭氏讓他坐下說：“你家大甥女有婆家沒有？”李立說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“前日有幾處提親不知允否，大約未允的多。老太太的意思我也猜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著了，只是富貴貧賤不同，如何作親？”鄭氏說：“你這話說錯了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奚家也是舊族，以先雖不算第一的富家，在南京也可數二三了，就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如今也還過得。只要你令姐不嫌我們就是了。”李立說：“求之不得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，哪有嫌的話。”鄭氏說：“就托你去作個媒。”李立答應著，一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>出來向奚家去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    李立回來，向鄭氏說：“老太太可以再等幾天，等他們商議商議</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”鄭氏說：“可是等你姐丈來家？”李立說：“不是的，姐丈一去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的時候，就向姐姐說兩個甥女大了，有可做的親，家里只管做，莫等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著我來家，我去還有幾年。”鄭氏說：“求親哪有太急的，等那邊有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>信，你再回我話罷。”李立說完了出去了。這原是李立一去說李氏就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>肯的，因李氏問了引香，引香不答應，又望了拾香一眼，他兩個就悄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>悄的去偷著抱頭而哭。李氏不知是何緣故，所以叫李立來回話不要遽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>允。李立過了幾天又去見李氏，李氏笑著向李立說：“這件事我倒沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>法，跟你商議商議看如何才好？”李立說：“是怎么樣？”李氏說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“引香跟拾香他兩個決不相舍，情願聚在一處，我想，豈有人家娶親</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娶兩個的？”李立聽了也不出聲，想了一會說：“等我去商議，看是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如何。”李氏說：“要是這樣才好，不是這樣，只怕又要難為人了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”李立答應著去了。來見鄭氏，把引香、拾香的情節細細的說了。鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏說：“好卻也好，不知嫣娘可肯。”說著丫頭去叫了嫣娘來，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了，鄭氏又向嫣娘前后說明，嫣娘說：“兒子的事總是母親作主。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”鄭氏知道他肯了，就叫李立明日請人擇日子吃茶，又商議娶的話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說：“這期服未滿，今年娶親我心里不安。”鄭氏說：“且看明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>年日子，遠近若是春季也可使得了。”嫣娘不敢再說，就答應著，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>坐一時出來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了園里，仍是天天悶悶的。不覺到季秋時候，嫣娘看園里菊花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>俱開，因幾回想去給富春掃墓，鄭氏不許，嫣娘就趁著菊花開時，叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人備了酒席并香紙等物，叫丫頭們將明月清風廬中間打掃了，擺上桌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子、供上供物，嫣娘領著宜人幾個上了香，又拜了幾拜，宜人幾個俱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>磕了頭。大家哭了一會，嫣娘說：“奶奶在日，最喜歡（原文下缺一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>頁）。”大家又慟哭一場。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了晚上，忽然秋雨淒淒，秋風颯颯，嫣娘叫點了燈，自己一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>往里間坐著，坐了一時又睡下，聽著外邊一時風，一時雨，一時寒鴉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>亂叫，一時草虫亂鳴，翻來覆去再睡不著，想道：“這真是睡不著如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>反掌了。”就在被里作了一個小調，哀哀吟著：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “風聲、雨聲，俱化作斷腸聲，虫鳴、鳥鳴，又鳴到三更，惹人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>傷情。叫俺隔著窗兒，怎聽到天明。睜著眼兒，目不轉睛，望那淒淒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>慘慘一個孤檠。這是有夢也夢不成，不時的愁暗生。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    吟了幾遍，看窗櫺上已白了，嫣娘方才朦朧睡去。不一時又醒了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，起來仍是長吁短嘆。雖然宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴、娟、嫿、關、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窈、么鳳天天伴著，也不能解悶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    不覺過了冬到了春天。鄭氏給他看〔親〕的日子是三月以內，吉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>期近了，鄭氏說：“這新房可以安在聊寄齋罷。”嫣娘說：“何必有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這些忌的，現在明月清風廬兩旁俱有櫥子，安上兩個新房恰好。”鄭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>氏也依了，就著人預先收拾了，叫宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴去處處住</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，叫娟、嫿、關、窈、么鳳去所所住。到了吉日，過了門，拜了堂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>各入洞房。到了晚上，吃了團圓酒，宜人跟阿粲商議說：“我們何不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去聽聽房間？娉婷、雁奴可去？”他兩個說：“我們還有甚么心腸去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聽房，你兩個去罷！”宜人同阿粲又到了所所邀他五個，娟姐不來；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫿姐也不來，說：“給娟姐作伴。”關關、窈窈、么鳳來了。先到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>引香那邊，宜人將舌尖兒舔破紅紙往里望，望著引香背著臉坐著，嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘站在跟前說：“姐姐今日不傷春了？”又說：“姐姐去了來了幾次</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，我到上房去看姐姐，姐姐總不理我，是怪我不成？”引香也不答應</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。嫣娘只得回來，坐了一時又起來剪剪蠟花，出來到拾香這邊。宜人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>幾個也到這邊窗前，么鳳用手指頭搗破窗紙，阿粲也搗破一塊望著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>拾香見嫣娘來，就上了床將帳子放下，坐在里邊，嫣娘說：“是了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這又是我得罪妹妹了。”作了一個揖。么鳳、阿粲忍不住笑，又拉拉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>宜人、關關、窈窈都來看，哪知地下青苔甚滑，你推我，我推你，急</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著去看，就都跌在地下大笑起來。嫣娘說：“這外邊還有人不成？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>哪知他們連忙跑了，嫣娘坐著，聽了一時不見動靜，想著莫是富春來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，想了一時又起來，到引香這邊來。卻一夜沒有閑著，一時到這邊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，一時到那邊。不知后來如何。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十四回  課藝  題圖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘一夜未睡，黎明在引香房里才隱幾而臥，一時又醒了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見引香也在那里坐著，嫣娘說：“姐姐如何不睡？”說著就起來到引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香跟前，將引香的手拉著說：“姐姐這個赤金蝦須（原文下缺三字）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>、翡翠鐲子是姐姐家里的舊物，是新制的？”引香也不答應，將手一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卷，鐲子碰著玎璫一響，嫣娘說：“這聲音倒是有趣。”引香微微一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>笑也不答應，嫣娘站著向引香望了一時就慢慢的出來。到拾香這邊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>見拾香和衣睡在床上，嫣娘自己說：“這暮春天氣，尚覺甚寒，如何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不蓋上被就睡了，不怕寒著嗎？”說著到床前輕輕將被替他蓋上，就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>坐在床沿，看著那臉如銀杏，映著這桃紅湖縐被，更顯嬌艷。又慢慢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的出來，到了院子里，順著步走到聊寄齋，見宜人他們一個也不在屋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>里，問丫頭他們哪里去了，丫頭說：“老太太叫去了。”嫣娘又回來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，到了攜艷館，娟、嫿幾個接著，進來坐下，么鳳說：“爺的尊冠給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我看看。”嫣娘就去下來遞給么鳳，么鳳接過來戴在自己頭上，笑著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>向關關作個揖說：“妹妹，是我得罪你了！”引著大家都笑起來。關</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>關說：“取下來罷！新郎莫裝新了。”么鳳笑著去下來還給嫣娘戴上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，大家說起昨日聽房內話，又笑起來。正在笑著，娉婷、雁奴來了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雁奴問說：“你們笑甚么？”大家將昨日作揖的話說了一遍，雁奴說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“這算甚么，不過是個半禮。以前我姑奶奶來，爺還施個全禮咧！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘聽著嘆了口氣，正要說話，關關、窈窈說：“先生來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘說：“哪個先生？”看著是宜人、阿粲進來了。嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他們如何稱你兩個是先生？”宜人說：“我雖不懂芙蓉典，就不能做</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>先生不成？”又向娟、嫿他們說：“上學罷。”他們都往里間去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雁奴就趁空向嫣娘小聲說：“老太太賞我好幾疋綾子，老太太說可憐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我跟姑奶奶一場，如今也成個孤人了。”嫣娘說：“好，這是老太太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>打狗看主面的意思。”雁奴瞅了嫣娘一眼，又小聲說：“人家好意對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你說，你倒罵我。且這是老太太賞我，如何說是打狗？這‘打’之一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>字，若是你還是做秀才，定要考個十二等。”嫣娘笑著說：“我回來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>給你賠不是，你莫說了。”又問宜人說：“老太太叫你做甚么？”宜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>人說：“老太太對我說的話我還未說，是老太太叫向他們說二位新奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奶的稱呼不好分別，叫我們照著長幼稱大奶奶、二奶奶就是了。”說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著，嫣娘看娟、嫿、關、窈抱琴的抱琴，拿簫的拿簫，拿筆硯的拿筆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>硯，都放在各處桌上。嫣娘說：“這是做甚么！”宜人說：“爺不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>道，我跟阿粲、么鳳做了掌教的了。他們跟我與阿粲學琴，跟么鳳學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>簫，么鳳又同他們跟我與阿粲學字。”嫣娘說：“我今日來閱個課，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>先考的是字、你們都寫，我挨次來看。”娉婷幾個就都研了墨，調了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>筆，周周正正坐著，伏在桌上去寫。嫣娘走去，看著娉婷寫，在旁邊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>指點了一會，又到娟姐。嫿姐處說了一會，又到關關、窈窈處看著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你兩個不是這樣寫法，我來把著你的手。”先把了關關，又把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>窈窈。窈窈把著卻手東一歪西一歪，嫣娘說：“你莫動，把筆拿住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”窈窈說：“你的手把著我的手痒痒的，我怎么不動？”嫣娘笑了笑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又把了一時。去看雁奴寫的，就偷偷的問雁奴說：“你姑奶奶的《</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>攜艷圖》，你可有收著？”雁奴說：“在我那里。”嫣娘說：“你去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>取來給我。”雁奴放下筆去了。嫣娘又看么鳳的字，說：“你像個會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>寫字的。”么鳳說：“我以先也學過，總是寫的不好。”嫣娘說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>就是這樣寫法，寫寫就好了。”看畢說：“這一場完了，再考那一場</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>罷。”問：“是誰學琴，是誰學簫？”宜人說：“是娟姐、窈姐、娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐學琴，是嫿姐、關姐、雁姐學簫。”嫣娘說：“一齊都彈起來，琴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>畢再吹簫。”宜人同阿粲教他三個彈了一會，又教了一會指法，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“你三個的泛音打的總不好，不是輕了就是重了，這泛音總要手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>靠著弦不離不即才可出音。”說著又叫么鳳教他們吹簫，么鳳說：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>雁姐沒在這里。”嫣娘說：“不用等他，就是他兩個吹罷。”么鳳教</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>著吹了一時，嫣娘說：“這‘凡’字轉‘乙’字，‘乙’字又轉‘工</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>’字總不自然，且欠脫卸之法。”說了一會，嫣娘看雁奴來了在門外</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>站著，嫣娘出來，雁奴將《攜艷圖》偷偷遞給他，嫣娘將袖子籠著去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    來到明月清風廬，先到了拾香屋里，坐下說：“你姊妹兩個有封</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>號了。”拾香說：“甚么封號？”嫣娘說：“母親說你姊妹兩個他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不好稱呼，叫論長幼稱你是二奶奶，你姐姐是大奶奶。”說著將袖中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>《攜艷圖》拿出來，說：“二姐姐將我這個畫兒收起，不必給大奶奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>知道。”又坐了一會，說了一會閑話。出來到引香屋里坐下說：“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如今是大奶奶了。”又把鄭氏的話告于他，引香說：“母親想的甚是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>周到，又費母親的心。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘就日日同著引香、拾香并宜人幾個談笑，不覺到夏末秋初，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘原想給富春作個周年，鄭氏不肯，且以嫣娘已經娶了引香、拾香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，怕他兩個忌諱，嫣娘就請了幾位高僧在靜因庵替他超度了幾日。嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘自是日日去敬禮焚香不必說了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，拾香在屋閑坐，想起來嫣娘交給他的畫，放了幾個月也未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>看看，又說莫給我姐姐看著，倒是個甚么畫兒？就起來將畫拿來展開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一看，看是富春的小照，宜人幾個俱在上邊，卻無有么鳳，想道：“</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這瞞著我姐姐甚么意思？”想了一會，想道：“是了，是怕我姐姐怪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他的意思，他也太有記性了，必是因那年我姐姐說愛博而情馳的話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”正在看著想著，不妨引香進來了，拾香卻不好收起，只得說：“姐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>姐來看看這個行樂圖。”引香看了一會，知是富春的小照，又嗟嘆了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一會，正在看著，嫣娘進來了。嫣娘卻不好再瞞的，只得說：“大奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奶看著，想是也不免有些酸鼻了。”引香說：“他在日我們本來甚好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，今日無了他，怎不叫人傷心！”又問嫣娘說：“這上邊俱有題贊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如何正主反沒有贊呢？”嫣娘說：“這是他自己畫的，自己題的，所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>以沒有他自己的贊。”引香就叫丫頭去拿了筆硯來，說：“我來品題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>品題。”嫣娘說：“很好，很好。”就替引香研了墨，引香拈起筆來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>題道，是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    自對妝台自寫真，誰知意屬畫中人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    芳情脈脈終無語，幽艷娟娟尚帶嚬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    爾向從前留面目，我由今日想精神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    可憐玉魄歸何處，此是前身是后身？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    題畢，嫣娘看了，又是夸好，又是傷心。引香正在拿著看，嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也在看，不覺一陣心酸，那淚落了幾點在引香手上。嫣娘去拭，引香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“莫拭，這點點是淚，卻點點是你的心血。”引香看完，將圖放</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>下。拾香說：“我作一聯，你兩個聽聽可好。是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    笑來惜惜知焉否</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    喚去真真應也無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不可天天將他們捫在心上當作一條正事，就是我們姐妹與你夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>唱婦隨值然燕婉之情亦不可太重了。”說到這里，嫣娘就低著頭不出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一聲，又嘆了兩口氣，也不顧他兩個在這里坐著，他就出來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一路走著，想富春在日是何等的溫柔，就是勸我也無如此搶白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一路走，一路想，不覺掉下淚來。到了處處那邊，看著那年送春的亭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>子，忽然想到如今是秋初了，明日我何不來作個迎秋的會，發泄發泄</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我胃中之悶。不知第二日作了沒作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十五回  迎秋  染病</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘想作迎秋會，站了一時，回來到引香房里坐下，引香說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我今日得罪你了。”嫣娘說：“大奶奶之言，誠為藥石，當銘心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不忘的，怎么說到得罪？不過是我一時心煩，未等說完我就走了，倒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是我得罪你了。只是法語之言能無從乎？卻要改之為貴，不知我可能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>改不能改，這卻連我自己也不能定，倒怕真負了你的心。”說著坐了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一時，天已晚了，引香說：“我今日心里不快，你到那邊歇歇去罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“使得。”又坐了一時去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了拾香房里，拾香說：“你怎么不在那邊，莫是我姐姐怪你，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>把你趕出來了？”嫣娘說：“不是怪我。”說著就嘆了口氣。拾香說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“姐姐之言也非無理。”嫣娘說：“我豈如此糊涂，不知話之好歹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？你想想他們幾個，如宜人、阿粲、娉婷，這幾個的來路你是知道的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，他們也可謂心如金石，當初我一見他們就兩下里如此纏綿，竟到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不能解的地位，這就可信他們是能共安樂即能共患難的了。”拾香說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“他三個且無論你花許多銀子，就是你的心也是費盡了。”嫣娘說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>：“我有個識英雄于風塵的眼光，這幾兩銀子算甚么？世上薄情的人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>未必無情，多是因這幾兩銀子慳慳吝吝，所以‘情’之一字就不知為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何物了。即如你家姐妹兩個，我以先在芙蓉花下任你兩個奚落，豈真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>我是個呆子！只是這惜花之情太重，所以就叫我是狗是馬，再等而下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>之，是魚是鱉，我都願意。”說著拾香笑起來說：“你方才說你不呆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，這呆話又出來了。”嫣娘說：“且莫講這些事了。我跟你商議明日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>作了迎秋會，你自然是去的，不知大奶奶可去不去？你可能替我代請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一請？”拾香說：“你怎么拿的穩我必去，我明日偏不去。你自己不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>敢去請客，我又不是你的小價，如何叫我去請？若是我不去，你可能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫你們大奶奶來請我？”嫣娘笑著說：“是我說錯了，我先負荊請罪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”說著又作了一個揖，把臉伸過去說：“請二奶奶打著問他還混說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>不混說了？”引的拾香大笑說：“你嘔死我了，那富春姐姐只怕就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你這樣嘔死的。”嫣娘說：“你倒公道之至，還想給前人出氣，我這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個臉更是該打的！”說著笑了一時。一時用了晚飯，又坐著談了一時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>明日迎秋的話，就歇了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了第二日，一早嫣娘起來，催著拾香去向引香說了，一齊都到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>亭子上去了。一時宜人幾個都來了。嫣娘叫人將席擺上，席擺了，嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘出了亭子，向西作了一揖說：“此間有一薄酌，請你這秋到里邊一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>談。”引的大家笑了。一會嫣娘進了亭子，坐下同引香、拾香、宜人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>幾個飲了一會酒，嫣娘就斟了一杯送在上面空座上，說：“你這秋年</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>年來的，卻是何意？說你有情，你卻把柳葉催黃了，蘆花逼白了，把</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>菊花、芙蓉、桂花都促著急急的落了，又把楓葉、柿葉都叫他變紅了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。你還怕人不傷心，又特特的把風颼颼的吹來，叫人冷冷清清；把雨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>霎霎的下著，叫人淒淒涼涼。我勸你不如早些回去罷，你又是不肯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>若說你無情，你又慣會動人的心，使那宋玉悲秋，杜牧傷秋，那老工</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>部也不免有些酸心無奈何了，反作了個《秋興八首》。你這秋，我說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你的可是不是？只怕你也沒的說了。”說著長嘆了一聲說：“噯，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>生如夢，今年迎秋，明年送春，不知不覺就雪上少年頭了。”說著就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嗚嗚咽咽哭起來了。正在哭著，忽然向后一仰，一下跌倒。引香幾個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>連忙扶起，叫著不應，就立刻連椅子抬著抬到引香房里，娉婷、雁奴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兩個駕到床上，引香說：“慢慢放下躺著。”宜人說：“不可平放著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，爺是一時傷感太過，氣痰上壅，放下就了不得了。”向著娉婷、雁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奴說：“你兩個快些上床，在后靠著，爺坐在床上罷。”引香又忙著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫丫頭去回老太太，宜人說：“暫且莫回，老太太年紀大了，聽著只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>怕一頭不了又一頭了，俟稍定一時，等爺能說出話來再去回罷。”引</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香只得依了。看著嫣娘臉上黃如金紙一般，引香、拾香叫著不應，娉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>婷、雁奴兩個在后靠著，引香、拾香兩個拉著他兩只手摸著脈，那脈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>先則亂跳，后則微微一動，引香、拾香說：“只怕是不中用了。”就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>放聲大哭，娉婷、雁奴也是大哭，娟、嫿、關、窈、阿粲、么鳳在地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>下站著俱是大哭。宜人高聲說：“莫哭，病人原是從傷心得的病，再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聽著哭更是要傷心了。”無奈哭聲太多，一時再叫不應，宜人沒了法</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，只得勸住引香，在耳跟前說了一會，又勸住了拾香，也說明了，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>勸住眾人才各各住了哭聲，一齊望望嫣娘。又過了一時，嫣娘的臉微</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>微一紅，眼微微一睜，就喉中哇然一聲吐出幾口痰帶血來。宜人說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“好了，阿彌陀佛！”引香、拾香問著可吃茶，嫣娘搖搖頭，引香又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫娟姐去燉人參膏子拿來，娟姐去了。嫣娘又嘆口氣把眼閉著，宜人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>說：“爺倒是靜養靜養好，此時可以躺下了。”娉婷、雁奴就輕輕將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘放下睡好，宜人又向嫿姐說：“你去回老太太知道，只說爺是偶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>冒風寒，不可太說重了。”嫿姐答應著去了。鄭氏聽說，連忙一手扶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>杖，一手扶著丫頭來了，嫿姐在后跟著也回來了。到了明月清風廬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>進了里間問嫣娘是怎么的，此時嫣娘心里已經明白了，聽鄭氏問他，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他就說：“沒甚病，不過是涼了。”鄭氏坐了一時說：“可用請郎中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>吃藥？”嫣娘說：“不用。”鄭氏又坐了一時去了。嫣娘雖然病減了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>些，只是閉著眼憩睡。過了十幾日，依然如是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    一日，引香、拾香因他父親來家了，家里來接，鄭氏說：“嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這些時也好些了，你兩個回家去看看罷。”引香、拾香見了嫣娘，向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘說了，嫣娘說：“你們回去替我請安罷，我不能去。”引香、拾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>香答應著去了。只有宜人在屋里，嫣娘向宜人說：“你知道我這病因</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>何而來？”宜人說：“是為亡的奶奶而來。”嫣娘說：“固然由此而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起，然我之心卻不專在這里。我想天下沒有不死的人，富春既然可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>先我而亡，如你們這兩位奶奶，就是你們幾個，又能常像個個是白發</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>到老的嗎？你們這些人的心，我卻知道不是那樹倒猢猻散的樣子，我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如今病著不能全好，你們依是照舊待我，‘士窮見節義，世亂知忠臣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>’，這才見你們的真心。最可恨的天下的人向暖的不肯向寒，你看那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>也有在一處天天親熱的了不得的，一旦失了勢，那玉山傾倒，他就不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>問了，或者倒翻過手來推他一下也未可定。你們這閨閣中人，雖不讀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聖賢之書，依我看來，前日我得病的時候，你們那樣的悲傷；我就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>死了，得你們慟哭一場，這也是你不負我，我不負你了，可以令世上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>須眉男子聽著，叫他慚愧無地。前日大奶奶勸我的話，與亡的奶奶臨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>終的囑咐說‘惜花的工夫不可太省了’，卻大不相同，可見人心不同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。這大奶奶哪知我惜花的心腸！”宜人說：“大奶奶之言卻也不錯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”嫣娘說：“錯是不錯，然不為我之知己。”正在說著，丫頭來說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“老太太叫宜姐。”宜姐說：“這屋里沒有人。”說著恰好娉婷、雁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>奴來了，宜人說：“你兩個在這里給爺作伴，我去看老太太叫我作甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么。”宜人去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫣娘叫雁奴、娉婷扶他躺下，又叫他兩個坐在床沿上，嫣娘說：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>“我如今是樂境變成苦境了。”說著那嗓子就說不出來，停了一刻，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>哭著說：“可憐誰知道我的苦，我這苦卻是叫我自己也說不上來的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>只好啞子吃了黃柏味，自己有苦自己知了。”娉婷也哭著說：“爺的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>病是不久就好的，何必傷心？”嫣娘說：“病之好與不好，我卻不問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他。只是這心病難醫，虧著有你們幾個，尚不是鑼鼓歇了、戲場散了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>的人，仍是把我時時放在心上，這也不枉我素日愛你們之情，你們也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是報答我了。”說著又哭了一會，又向雁奴說：“你可想你姑奶奶？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”說到“姑奶奶”三個字就聲淚俱下，雁奴也是哭，娉婷在旁邊給嫣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>娘拭著淚也是哭，雁奴說：“姑奶奶可恨死的太早了！若是留下個哥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兒、姐兒，也可給爺寬寬心，可憐竟是梅花開了一樹空花了。”嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>聽到這里，更是慟不可言，哭著說：“總是我沒福，連累了你姑奶奶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，還說甚么？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    正在哭著，宜人來了，嫣娘止住了哭，問他：“老太太叫你作甚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>么？”宜人說：“老太太說他老了，家里的事也多，外面雖有李大爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>照應，內邊總要我煩心，你們兩個奶奶也未必能操這個心。我看你這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>孩子還可以中用，你又識字，又通個文理、算盤都是會的，定事交給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>你罷。爺想想我如何能有這樣才干，這是老太太的命，我也不敢不遵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，只得受下了。”嫣娘說：“老太太自然看你可以承當的，才交給你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，你受了這責任，老太太天天可以靜養靜養，也是你替我盡了孝心了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。”說著引香、拾香回來了，進了屋坐下，宜人又將老太太的話告于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他兩個知道，說完又到上房去了。不知嫣娘之病好了沒好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>         第十六回  夢覺  情釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    話說嫣娘之病仍是未好，過幾日輕些，過幾日重些。引香、拾香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>同娉婷、阿粲幾個天天守著，宜人常在上房照料，得空即來看嫣娘，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>鄭氏也常常來看。一日，宜人上房的事完了，來看嫣娘，回到聊寄齋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，這時天已晚了，就在屋里坐了一時，看月明如畫，就慢慢的走到那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>送春迎秋的亭子上，對著明月長嘆了幾聲，想到爺的病總是這天公害</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了他了，就望空拜了幾拜說：“老天你何必害人太甚！若是你愛嫣娘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，叫他有這樣聰明，有這樣性情，你就不該從聰明、性情上叫他生出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>這樣病來。你既叫他有這樣聰明、有這樣性情，又叫他從這聰明、性</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>情上生出這樣病來，這不是你愛他反害了他嗎？倒不若你以先不叫他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>有這樣聰明，有這樣性情，他倒不得這樣病了。你想他這個人害了這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個病，若是死了，他如何是死得的？上頭有老太太是年近古稀，豈可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>白發喪明？下邊有這兩個奶奶，是青年雛鳳，豈可叫他做個泣孤舟之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫠婦？就是我們這幾個婢子，也是痴心太重，想得個花叢柳岸的主人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，又豈可叫我們作了個九月荷花、落一陣雨打的殘聲了！”說著就哭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起來了，又說：“老天你若是真愛嫣娘，愛人到要愛到底，才見你愛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>嫣娘的意思不是假的。他如今得了這個病，你不救救他，誰個能救救</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>他？”又哭了一時，覺冷露濕衣，夜氣逼人，就慢慢的回來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻說嫣娘日日病著，這一夜睡下，到交四更方才朦朧睡去，忽見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>一和尚推門而入，直至床前，向頂上拍了一下說：“色即是空，空即</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>是色，你就忘了不成？”那和尚鑽進被來就不見了。嫣娘猛然驚醒，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>卻是一夢。看殘燈灺灺，聽引香翻身，他也沒有言語，就想道他小時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>候作了一夢，夢見了許多的美人，有一美人作的詞尚全記得，就小聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>吟著：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “天上人間，可憐誰是有緣、誰是無緣？到頭來，都是一般參了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>個沒要緊的禪，才笑人枉然。作一對鴛鴦睡，誰知我，也是空纏綿。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    念了幾遍，即覺心地光明，看看窗上白了，也不用人扶著，就自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>己起來穿了衣服，下了床。引香也醒了，說：“你如何自己能起來了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>？”嫣娘也不答應，走到窗前，將筆硯拿過來，研了墨，拈起筆來寫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>道是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    未熟黃梁夢已休，殷勤費盡后何求？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    朝來磨得青鋒劍，斬斷今今古古愁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫畢投筆于地，拍手大笑，又跑在外邊叫人將“明月清風廬”的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>匾放下來，叫丫頭磨了墨，鋪上紙，拿了大筆寫道，是：“抱月披風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>廬”。寫畢叫人立刻換上。一時引香、拾香俱起來了，嫣娘又叫丫頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>去叫宜人、阿粲、娉婷、雁奴、娟、嫿、關、窈、么鳳都來，并各將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>琴簫帶來，一時俱來了。嫣娘就坐在上面，叫引香、拾香坐在兩邊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>叫宜人幾個坐在下手，俱各彈起琴來，吹起簫來。嫣娘在上面坐著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>拍幾而歌，歌道是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    “天地之大兮，何者為吾之所有？天地之遠兮，今從天外而回首</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>。我已無愁兮，何須此（酉彔）（酉彔）醛醾之酒？即飲一石兮，或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>飲一斗亦不過。若蒼松翠柏兮，偶爾與居而與友。說甚為將兮，功烈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>而不朽？說甚為相兮，綰金紫與青緩？無懮愁之神仙兮，與我而左右</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>；無挂礙之維摩兮，與我而前后。任花開花落兮，我無所于掣肘；任</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>春去秋來兮，我不必于援手。朝朝暮暮兮，惟戴高而履厚。問我何樂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>兮，我則曰否否！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    歌畢又大笑幾聲，叫他們住了琴簫說：“我這個明月清風廬，當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>日大奶奶給我題的，原是怕我到風月場中，忘了這月是本明的，風是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>本清的。我如今抱的是月，披的是風，這‘明、清’二字我才領略過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>來了。只是天下的人哪有不愛風月的？我之所謂風月，卻不是花街柳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>巷中的春色，秦樓楚館中的韶光。若是那以金買笑的人，則不是愛風</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>月的情種，卻是伴風月的情奴耳！然我之得有這番風月妙趣，若不是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>遇著你們這些月里嫦娥、風中楊柳，我就有這愛風月的心腸也用不著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，可見是上天成全我了。我如今又長了一番學問，凡鐘情的溺于情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，為情溺了卻不是善于鐘情了。‘情’之一字出于先天鐘情而不溺情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，才不傷這‘情’字本來的面目。我卻是由鐘情而至于溺情，由溺情</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>而又反于鐘情，情中之溺歷，我可以自負，這深深淺淺、濃濃淡淡是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>深知的了。”正在說著，引香、拾香、宜人幾個俱勸說：“爺是才好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>了，不可太受勞了。”嫣娘也就坐著不言語了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    以后嫣娘也無心仕路，日日同引香諸人嘯月嘲風，優游自樂，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>起個別號為“大覺先生”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">         跋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    先生中州戈陽舊族也，姓吳氏，諱貽棠，字蔭南，愛存其號也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>與先君為莫逆交。鈺當總角，先君即命鈺依先生側，曰：“子其事之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>如吾可也。”鈺欣然應之唯唯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    先生視鈺如己子，令來入家塾讀，凡衣食之類無不過厚焉。后先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>君見背，先生更厚視之。及先生仕長蘆，鈺以家事故未得隨往。先生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>歸田越數載，先王之嫡配任母捐世次年，先生續弦于周。周母來歸，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>其間繁冗多故，皆命鈺為之。又次年，先生抱手足恙，不獲出入自隨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>，每日寂坐小齋，先生不能〔一〕時舍鈺，鈺亦不忍一時違先生也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>    然先生為人，好脫略，性豪邁，常對令窗矩榻，咄咄不自得，因</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>編《可是夢》、《風月鑒》二種以為消遣。書成，親友索觀之，俱喚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>為靜者心多妙也。鈺思先生生平，其卓卓者若是，固今之不可多見，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>而以病廢，惜哉！悲哉！但其人不可不使，不借書以何之，烏知先生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>期頤，后人盡得識先生為何如人耶？鈺堂弟存智為先生理家計，時居</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>其家，鈺與商之，付諸剞劂，庶存先生一時之無聊寄慨云爾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>                                         寄男方鈺謹識</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/74a8951dddc07a7a/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Feng Yueh Jiann, by Yi Tarng Wu</p></div>"
        },
