            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-f09fcd twpub-74a8951dddc07a7a-6b4cd0\"><p>This Web site includes information about Project Gutenberg-tm,\nincluding how to make donations to the Project Gutenberg Literary\nArchive Foundation, how to help produce our new eBooks, and how to\nsubscribe to our email newsletter to hear about new eBooks.</p></div>"
